Dialogue: 3,0:00:22.24,0:00:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一千万卢比支付给了尊敬的纳拉辛哈·拉奥 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:22.24,0:00:26.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Money, rupees one crore was paid to honourable P.V. Narasimha Rao...
Dialogue: 3,0:00:27.08,0:00:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度总理
Dialogue: 2,0:00:27.08,0:00:28.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the Prime Minister of India.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:29.16,0:00:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他只是在兜售谎言，就像他一直做的那样..
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.16,0:00:31.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He's just selling lies, as he has always done...
Dialogue: 3,0:00:32.56,0:00:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}把媒体的注意力从骗局转移到首相身上
Dialogue: 2,0:00:32.56,0:00:36.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...to divert the media's attention from the scam to the Prime Minister.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:37.20,0:00:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这不是“哈尔沙德 · 梅塔骗局” ，而是“ p.v. 纳拉辛哈 · 拉奥骗局”
Dialogue: 2,0:00:37.20,0:00:43.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It is not the 'Harshad Mehta scam'. It is the 'P.V. Narasimha Rao scam'.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:43.92,0:00:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果双方继续发表声明，可能很快就会出问题
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.92,0:00:49.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And if both sides keep giving statements, problems may arise.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:49.68,0:00:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[苏切塔]“即使哈沙德在撒谎，他也在诋毁当权者的形象... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.68,0:00:53.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'Even if Harshad was lying, he was denting the image of those in power...'
Dialogue: 3,0:00:53.48,0:00:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... 每个人都知道有必要解决这个问题”
Dialogue: 2,0:00:53.48,0:00:56.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...and everyone was aware that a solution was necessary.'
Dialogue: 3,0:01:00.08,0:01:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔先生，你说你有一张去首相官邸访客证
Dialogue: 2,0:01:00.08,0:01:02.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr. Mehta, you said, that you have a visiting slip...
Dialogue: 3,0:01:02.12,0:01:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 日期是11月4日
Dialogue: 2,0:01:02.12,0:01:05.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...dated 4th November, for the Prime Minister's residence.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:05.64,0:01:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，没错
Dialogue: 2,0:01:05.64,0:01:06.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes. That is right.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:07.88,0:01:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是我找不到那张纸条
Dialogue: 2,0:01:07.88,0:01:09.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I can't find that slip.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:10.52,0:01:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你自相矛盾..
Dialogue: 2,0:01:10.52,0:01:13.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Das] If you contradict yourself...
Dialogue: 3,0:01:14.12,0:01:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就没有任何理由反对首相
Dialogue: 2,0:01:14.12,0:01:16.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...you don't really have any case against the Prime Minister.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:18.92,0:01:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我希望你能理解”
Dialogue: 2,0:01:18.92,0:01:20.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Das] 'I hope you understand.'
Dialogue: 3,0:01:22.12,0:01:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}奇怪的是，哈沙德开始自相矛盾
Dialogue: 2,0:01:22.12,0:01:24.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'Curiously, Harshad began to contradict himself.'
Dialogue: 3,0:01:24.88,0:01:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他对首相的指控永远无法得到证实... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:01:24.88,0:01:29.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'His claims and accusations against the Prime Minister could never be proven...'
Dialogue: 3,0:01:31.72,0:01:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他说，哈沙德是不是想把让首相下台作为交易的一部分? 没人知道
Dialogue: 2,0:01:31.72,0:01:35.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Was Harshad trying to let off the PM as part of a deal? Nobody knows.'
Dialogue: 3,0:01:35.92,0:01:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“但事情最终以失败告终，哈尔沙德也从未因贩卖毒品而被起诉”
Dialogue: 2,0:01:35.92,0:01:40.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'But the matter fizzled out. Harshad was never charged for dealing in narcotics.'
Dialogue: 3,0:01:40.84,0:01:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但现在，哈沙德被禁止进入股市... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:01:40.84,0:01:43.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'But now, Harshad was banned from the stock market...'
Dialogue: 3,0:01:43.44,0:01:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 市场继续暴跌
Dialogue: 2,0:01:43.44,0:01:45.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...and the market continued its free-fall.'
Dialogue: 3,0:01:45.92,0:01:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sensex 指数从1992年4月的4461点开始下跌... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:01:45.92,0:01:50.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'The Sensex dropped from 4461 in April 1992...'
Dialogue: 3,0:01:50.56,0:01:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}跌到2000点
Dialogue: 2,0:01:50.56,0:01:52.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...to 2000.'
Dialogue: 3,0:01:53.00,0:01:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那些在市场崩盘中失去一切的人... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:01:53.00,0:01:55.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Those who had lost everything in the market crash...'
Dialogue: 3,0:01:55.96,0:01:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“对他们来说... ... 哈沙德 · 梅塔真的是个骗子... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:01:55.96,0:01:59.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...for them... Harshad Mehta was really a liar...'
Dialogue: 3,0:02:28.20,0:02:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}已经通知了警方
Dialogue: 2,0:02:28.20,0:02:31.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The police have been informed.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:35.24,0:02:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你只需要在这里签字
Dialogue: 2,0:02:35.24,0:02:36.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You just need to sign here.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:40.84,0:02:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他为什么在这里？
Dialogue: 2,0:02:40.84,0:02:41.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why is he here?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:43.64,0:02:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让他离开
Dialogue: 2,0:02:43.64,0:02:44.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ask him to leave.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:49.48,0:02:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是怎么发生的？
Dialogue: 2,0:02:49.48,0:02:50.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How did this happen?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:54.16,0:02:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}(拉希尔的妻子)“为什么会发生这样的事? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:02:54.16,0:02:55.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Rahil's wife] 'How did it happen?'
Dialogue: 3,0:02:59.56,0:03:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不知道
Dialogue: 2,0:02:59.56,0:03:00.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't know.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:03.64,0:03:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不知道？
Dialogue: 2,0:03:03.64,0:03:04.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You don't know?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:08.36,0:03:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你什么都知道
Dialogue: 2,0:03:08.36,0:03:09.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You knew everything.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:11.48,0:03:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}(拉希尔的妻子)“你是最聪明的，不是吗? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:03:11.48,0:03:12.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Rahil's wife] 'You were the smartest, weren't you?'
Dialogue: 3,0:03:15.48,0:03:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我男人
Dialogue: 2,0:03:15.48,0:03:16.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This man...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:18.60,0:03:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他什么都不知道
Dialogue: 2,0:03:18.60,0:03:19.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...he didn't know anything.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:22.00,0:03:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每当我问起..
Dialogue: 2,0:03:22.00,0:03:22.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Whenever I asked...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:23.72,0:03:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他会说“哈沙德知道，哈沙德知道一切”
Dialogue: 2,0:03:23.72,0:03:26.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...he would say, "Harshad knows. Harshad knows everything".
Dialogue: 3,0:03:30.88,0:03:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}告诉我哈沙德大哥
Dialogue: 2,0:03:30.88,0:03:32.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, tell me Harshad Bhai.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:34.84,0:03:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是谁杀了他？
Dialogue: 2,0:03:34.84,0:03:35.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who killed him?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在你看来，这可能像是自杀
Dialogue: 2,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It may look like suicide to you.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:47.60,0:03:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但事实是你杀了他
Dialogue: 2,0:03:47.60,0:03:48.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But the truth is, you killed him.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你毁了他
Dialogue: 2,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You destroyed him.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:57.80,0:03:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 算了吧-你在很久以前就杀了他
Dialogue: 2,0:03:57.80,0:03:59.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Let it be. - You had killed him a long time ago.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:59.64,0:04:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只是今天才办葬礼
Dialogue: 2,0:03:59.64,0:04:02.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Today is just the funeral.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:04.20,0:04:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着! 他不是唯一一个
Dialogue: 2,0:04:04.20,0:04:06.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And listen! He's not the only one.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:08.92,0:04:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你杀过很多像他这样的人
Dialogue: 2,0:04:08.92,0:04:12.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You've killed many people like him.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:15.16,0:04:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们按照你的承诺投资了
Dialogue: 2,0:04:15.16,0:04:16.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We invested money on your word.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:18.04,0:04:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}(拉希尔的妻子)“我们信任你，而现在... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:04:18.04,0:04:19.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Rahil's wife] 'We trusted you and...'
Dialogue: 3,0:04:20.04,0:04:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你却说你不知道？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.04,0:04:21.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...you say, you don't know?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:23.00,0:04:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不知道什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:23.00,0:04:24.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What don't you know?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不知道什么！
Dialogue: 2,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What do you not know!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:34.00,0:05:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}景色不错
Dialogue: 2,0:05:34.00,0:05:34.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's a nice view.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:37.56,0:05:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，景色很美
Dialogue: 2,0:05:37.56,0:05:38.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes, the view is beautiful.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:40.56,0:05:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不在家的时候，一定错过了很多美景吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:40.56,0:05:43.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}When you were away from home, you must have missed this view?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:45.56,0:05:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是指我在监狱里的时候
Dialogue: 2,0:05:45.56,0:05:46.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You mean, when I was in jail.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:51.08,0:05:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}风景是次要的，但我确实错过了我的观点
Dialogue: 2,0:05:51.08,0:05:53.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Not this view, but I did miss my point of view.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:56.32,0:05:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为我的观点从未被发表出来
Dialogue: 2,0:05:56.32,0:05:58.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because my point of view was never printed/ captured.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:01.48,0:06:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来吧
Dialogue: 2,0:06:01.48,0:06:02.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:02.32,0:06:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在我们开始之前，吃点零食吧
Dialogue: 2,0:06:02.32,0:06:04.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Have some snacks, before we start.'
Dialogue: 3,0:06:05.24,0:06:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}中央调查局和税务部门非常喜欢我们的零食，所以..
Dialogue: 2,0:06:05.24,0:06:08.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}CBI and IT are so fond of our snacks that...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有时候他们突袭我只是为了吃点零食
Dialogue: 2,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...sometimes they raid me just to eat some snacks.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:10.64,0:06:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我能把它放在这儿吗?-当然
Dialogue: 2,0:06:10.64,0:06:12.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Can I keep it here? - Sure.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:14.00,0:06:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你们的口味相似，所以我相信你们也会喜欢的
Dialogue: 2,0:06:14.00,0:06:17.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And your taste is similar. So, I'm sure you'll like it too.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:19.08,0:06:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你似乎很了解我
Dialogue: 2,0:06:19.08,0:06:21.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You seem to know a lot about me.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:23.92,0:06:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在市场上，你必须同时关注你的朋友和敌人
Dialogue: 2,0:06:23.92,0:06:26.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In the market, you've to keep a tab on both friends and enemies.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:26.68,0:06:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，我是朋友还是敌人？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:26.68,0:06:28.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, am I a friend or an enemy?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:30.56,0:06:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你最清楚不过了
Dialogue: 2,0:06:30.56,0:06:31.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You know that best.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:33.64,0:06:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想你很快也会知道的
Dialogue: 2,0:06:33.64,0:06:35.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I think you'll know it soon too.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:35.96,0:06:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我确定
Dialogue: 2,0:06:35.96,0:06:36.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm sure.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:38.60,0:06:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我们可以开始了吗?-好的..
Dialogue: 2,0:06:38.60,0:06:41.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Shall we start? - Yes...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:47.76,0:06:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔先生你是普通人心目中的英雄
Dialogue: 2,0:06:47.76,0:06:50.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, Mr. Mehta, you were the common man's hero.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:50.12,0:06:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}市场上很多人都信任你
Dialogue: 2,0:06:50.12,0:06:52.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And many people in the market trusted you.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:52.80,0:06:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是当你不在的时候他们失去了信任
Dialogue: 2,0:06:52.80,0:06:55.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But then, when you were away, they lost their trust...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:55.16,0:06:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们失去了毕生的积蓄，有些人甚至失去了生命
Dialogue: 2,0:06:55.16,0:06:58.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...they lost their life savings, and a few of them even lost their lives.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:58.88,0:07:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，考虑到人们因为你而丧失市场信心
Dialogue: 2,0:06:58.88,0:07:01.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, what do you feel given the losses that people faced because of you...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:01.96,0:07:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}面临的损失，你有什么感想..
Dialogue: 2,0:07:01.96,0:07:04.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The loss of confidence in the market...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:04.84,0:07:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可以挽回吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:04.84,0:07:07.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...can it be restored?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:07.76,0:07:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我问你这个是因为... 如果你能回到市场..
Dialogue: 2,0:07:07.76,0:07:11.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm asking you this because... if you are able to return to the market...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:11.60,0:07:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你能解决这个危机吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:11.60,0:07:13.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...can you resolve this crisis?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你还有能力吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you still capable of it?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:19.40,0:07:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你看..
Dialogue: 2,0:07:19.40,0:07:20.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You see...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:21.32,0:07:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是一个误会
Dialogue: 2,0:07:21.32,0:07:22.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There is a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:23.52,0:07:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我没那么大能力
Dialogue: 2,0:07:23.52,0:07:24.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I am not that capable.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我真的没有
Dialogue: 2,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I really am not.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:28.68,0:07:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}事实上，我想删除这个“我”部分
Dialogue: 2,0:07:28.68,0:07:31.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In fact, I want to remove this "I" part of it.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:32.68,0:07:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我从来没有说过我有这样的能力
Dialogue: 2,0:07:32.68,0:07:35.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have never said that I'm so capable.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:36.52,0:07:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:07:36.52,0:07:37.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Look...'
Dialogue: 3,0:07:37.96,0:07:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我知道，很多人因为我而承受巨大的损失
Dialogue: 2,0:07:37.96,0:07:41.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'I know, many people have faced huge losses because of me.'
Dialogue: 3,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}尽管事实上..
Dialogue: 2,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In spite of the fact...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:43.36,0:07:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我和市场下跌没有直接关系
Dialogue: 2,0:07:43.36,0:07:45.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that I have nothing to do with the market fall directly.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们一直有个原则..
Dialogue: 2,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We always had a policy...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:50.56,0:07:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有人会因为我们而遭受损失
Dialogue: 2,0:07:50.56,0:07:52.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that no one must incur a loss because of us.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:54.20,0:07:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}任何个人和银行都不应该因为哈尔沙德 · 梅塔而受到影响
Dialogue: 2,0:07:54.20,0:07:57.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No individual and bank should suffer because of the dues...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:58.40,0:07:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德 · 梅塔而受到影响
Dialogue: 2,0:07:58.40,0:07:59.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...of Harshad Mehta.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:00.20,0:08:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你想让我相信这个？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:00.20,0:08:03.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You want me to believe this?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:03.44,0:08:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你想让我相信..
Dialogue: 2,0:08:03.44,0:08:04.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You want me to believe...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:04.68,0:08:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你对你给小投资者造成的损失感到内疚
Dialogue: 2,0:08:04.68,0:08:08.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that you feel guilty for the losses you caused to small investors.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:08.64,0:08:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真的吗，梅塔先生？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:08.64,0:08:09.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Really, Mr. Mehta?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:11.92,0:08:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，我把我的感受告诉你了，我表达了我的内疚
Dialogue: 2,0:08:11.92,0:08:15.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, I told you what I feel. I expressed my guilt.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:15.96,0:08:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}信不信由你
Dialogue: 2,0:08:15.96,0:08:18.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Believing it or not, is up to you.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:20.12,0:08:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不能强迫你相信这个
Dialogue: 2,0:08:20.12,0:08:21.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I can't force you to believe this.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:22.60,0:08:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}尽管如此，我还是希望你相信
Dialogue: 2,0:08:22.60,0:08:23.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Though, I would like you to believe.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:25.80,0:08:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果是关于损失那么..
Dialogue: 2,0:08:25.80,0:08:27.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And if it's about losses, then...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:28.40,0:08:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我也很痛苦，不是吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:28.40,0:08:29.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...I am suffering too, aren't I?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:38.08,0:08:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只有一个办法可以尽快解决这个问题
Dialogue: 2,0:08:38.08,0:08:41.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There's only one way to resolve this matter as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:41.88,0:08:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们将要求特别法庭
Dialogue: 2,0:08:41.88,0:08:44.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We'll request the special court...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:45.08,0:08:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}解决所有索赔
Dialogue: 2,0:08:45.08,0:08:47.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that we're ready to settle all the claims.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:49.32,0:08:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}和解委员会会处理好一切的
Dialogue: 2,0:08:49.32,0:08:51.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'The settlement commission will take care of everything.'
Dialogue: 3,0:08:52.16,0:08:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们有权给予豁免
Dialogue: 2,0:08:52.16,0:08:56.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And they have all the powers to grant immunity.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:57.76,0:08:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果委员会
Dialogue: 2,0:08:57.76,0:08:59.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If the commission agrees...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:00.24,0:09:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}被说服了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:00.24,0:09:01.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...gets convinced...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:01.60,0:09:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你所有的财产都会解冻
Dialogue: 2,0:09:01.60,0:09:04.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...all your assets will be released.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:06.12,0:09:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是，梅塔先生..
Dialogue: 2,0:09:06.12,0:09:08.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'But, Mr. Mehta...'
Dialogue: 3,0:09:08.68,0:09:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}请不要和这些财产扯上关系
Dialogue: 2,0:09:08.68,0:09:11.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...please don't get attached to these assets.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:14.36,0:09:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}最近，特别法庭对我的财产比我对我的财产更加重视
Dialogue: 2,0:09:14.36,0:09:17.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}These days, the special court is more attached to my assets than I am.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:29.96,0:09:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个 CBI..
Dialogue: 2,0:09:29.96,0:09:30.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This CBI...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:31.60,0:09:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}难道他们就没别的事可做吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:31.60,0:09:33.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do they have nothing better to do?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:34.28,0:09:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们又提出了一个新的指控
Dialogue: 2,0:09:34.28,0:09:35.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now, they've slapped a new case.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:36.96,0:09:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Bhushan ]“这是起诉书”
Dialogue: 2,0:09:36.96,0:09:39.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Bhushan] 'This is the charge sheet.'
Dialogue: 3,0:09:40.84,0:09:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们只是不想让我们摆脱这些案子
Dialogue: 2,0:09:40.84,0:09:43.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They just don't want us to get out of these cases.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:44.88,0:09:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们一听说和解委员会的事
Dialogue: 2,0:09:44.88,0:09:46.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}As soon as they heard about the settlement commission...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:46.28,0:09:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就用起诉书威胁我们
Dialogue: 2,0:09:46.28,0:09:47.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...they're threatening us with charge sheets.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:47.84,0:09:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想让我们闭嘴
Dialogue: 2,0:09:47.84,0:09:48.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They want to silence us.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:48.68,0:09:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这太荒谬了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:48.68,0:09:50.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is ridiculous enough to give fever to a donkey.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:52.32,0:09:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们说和解委员会为了将来的起诉
Dialogue: 2,0:09:52.32,0:09:54.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They say, settlement commissions can grant immunity...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可以给予的豁免权
Dialogue: 2,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...only for future prosecutions.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:56.68,0:09:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Bhushan ]“不适用于正在审理的案件”
Dialogue: 2,0:09:56.68,0:09:57.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Bhushan] 'Not for ongoing cases.'
Dialogue: 3,0:10:00.32,0:10:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}毫无疑问，CBI 以独特的方式处理了我的案子
Dialogue: 2,0:10:00.32,0:10:03.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'There's no doubt that CBI has handled my case in a unique manner.'
Dialogue: 3,0:10:04.00,0:10:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}独特的方式？
Dialogue: 2,0:10:04.00,0:10:04.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Unique manner?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:05.36,0:10:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你觉得自己被歧视了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:10:05.36,0:10:07.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You feel like you've been discriminated against?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:07.44,0:10:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，我受到了歧视
Dialogue: 2,0:10:07.44,0:10:09.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes, I have been discriminated against.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:10.20,0:10:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看看我的案子
Dialogue: 2,0:10:10.20,0:10:11.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Just look at my case.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:11.68,0:10:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就我而言，他们已经起诉了我的整个家庭
Dialogue: 2,0:10:11.68,0:10:13.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In my case, they have notified my entire family.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:14.56,0:10:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我以前从没见过，你可以自己看看
Dialogue: 2,0:10:14.56,0:10:17.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have never seen that before. You can check for yourself.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:19.60,0:10:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在，我没有任何资产.. ... 事实上
Dialogue: 2,0:10:19.60,0:10:22.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Today, I am left without any assets or money... virtually.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而且他们已经起诉了我很多次了
Dialogue: 2,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Plus, they've filed so many cases against me.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:25.68,0:10:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}通常，每个案件都有一个报告
Dialogue: 2,0:10:25.68,0:10:27.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Usually, every case has one FIR.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:27.28,0:10:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是当涉及到我的时候，他们就在每个案件中提交了7个报告
Dialogue: 2,0:10:27.28,0:10:29.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But when it comes to me, they've filed seven FIRs in every case.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:31.08,0:10:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}(哈沙德)“看看我身后的机构数量吧”
Dialogue: 2,0:10:31.08,0:10:32.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'And look at the number of agencies going behind me.'
Dialogue: 3,0:10:34.32,0:10:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}RBI，CBI，IT，ED，JPC...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:34.32,0:10:37.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}RBI, CBI, IT, ED, JPC...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:38.84,0:10:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所得税部门甚至提出了这样一个大案子
Dialogue: 2,0:10:38.84,0:10:40.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The Income Tax Department filed such a big case.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:41.92,0:10:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一千亿卢比
Dialogue: 2,0:10:41.92,0:10:43.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ten thousand crores.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:43.92,0:10:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就很离谱
Dialogue: 2,0:10:43.92,0:10:44.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Isn't that ridiculous?'
Dialogue: 3,0:10:48.16,0:10:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但你知道我最大的罪过是什么吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:10:48.16,0:10:50.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But, you know what my biggest crime is?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:52.72,0:10:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我最大的罪过就是，我是哈沙德 · 梅塔
Dialogue: 2,0:10:52.72,0:10:53.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That I'm Harshad Mehta.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:06.20,0:11:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[哈沙德]‘你为什么老是看这些法律书? ’
Dialogue: 2,0:11:06.20,0:11:08.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Why are you rubbing your nose in these law books?'
Dialogue: 3,0:11:10.32,0:11:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你打算退出生意圈，成为一名律师吗
Dialogue: 2,0:11:10.32,0:11:12.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Are you planning to quit the business and become a lawyer?'
Dialogue: 3,0:11:14.12,0:11:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}生意？
Dialogue: 2,0:11:14.12,0:11:15.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Business?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:16.96,0:11:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么生意？
Dialogue: 2,0:11:16.96,0:11:17.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What business?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:18.84,0:11:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}兄弟，现在只有我们懂法律，才有机会
Dialogue: 2,0:11:18.84,0:11:21.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bhai, now only we know the law, do we stand a chance.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:22.68,0:11:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}考虑到我们的处境..
Dialogue: 2,0:11:22.68,0:11:23.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because, given our situation...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:24.40,0:11:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果不成为律师，我们就不能做生意了
Dialogue: 2,0:11:24.40,0:11:26.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...if we don't become lawyers, we won't be able to do business.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:28.32,0:11:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[阿什温]“我们要为 CBI 的案子辩护”
Dialogue: 2,0:11:28.32,0:11:30.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ashwin] 'We have the CBI cases to defend.'
Dialogue: 3,0:11:31.04,0:11:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}税务部门一次又一次的处罚，我们都要辩护
Dialogue: 2,0:11:31.04,0:11:34.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}IT department is slapping penalty after penalty. We've to defend that.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:35.20,0:11:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有我们的保管人
Dialogue: 2,0:11:35.20,0:11:36.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And our custodian...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:37.28,0:11:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他的数学真是一塌糊涂
Dialogue: 2,0:11:37.28,0:11:38.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ashwin] 'His math is all over the place.'
Dialogue: 3,0:11:39.32,0:11:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他的办公室连账都算不明白
Dialogue: 2,0:11:39.32,0:11:41.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'His office has not even done the accounting correctly.'
Dialogue: 3,0:11:42.64,0:11:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}布尚说，他们低估了我们所有的资产
Dialogue: 2,0:11:42.64,0:11:45.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bhushan was saying, they've undervalued all our assets.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}该死的白痴
Dialogue: 2,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bloody idiots.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:48.44,0:11:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“让保管人做他想做的事吧”
Dialogue: 2,0:11:48.44,0:11:50.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Let the custodian do what he wishes.'
Dialogue: 3,0:11:52.00,0:11:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让他来设定价值
Dialogue: 2,0:11:52.00,0:11:53.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let him set the values.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:53.80,0:11:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}托管人本身是没有价值的
Dialogue: 2,0:11:53.80,0:11:55.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The custodian is value-less himself.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:01.04,0:12:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道我怎么想的吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:12:01.04,0:12:02.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You know what I think?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:03.36,0:12:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在是开始尝试新业务的正确时机
Dialogue: 2,0:12:03.36,0:12:05.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is the right time to start something new.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:08.40,0:12:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}继续
Dialogue: 2,0:12:08.40,0:12:09.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:10.84,0:12:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}开始一些新的事情
Dialogue: 2,0:12:10.84,0:12:11.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Start something new.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:13.36,0:12:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但这一次，问题不仅仅是我们的资产或金钱
Dialogue: 2,0:12:13.36,0:12:16.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But this time, it's not just a matter of our assets or of money.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:18.56,0:12:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们的名声岌岌可危，哈沙德
Dialogue: 2,0:12:18.56,0:12:19.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Our name is at stake, Harshad.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:24.00,0:12:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当“纳胡”变得富有，人们开始叫他“纳萨拉”
Dialogue: 2,0:12:24.00,0:12:26.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}When 'Nathhu' gets rich, people start calling him 'Nathalal'.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一旦我们有了钱，名声就会随之而来
Dialogue: 2,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Once we have money, the name will follow.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:31.08,0:12:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这不是获取名声的方式了
Dialogue: 2,0:12:31.08,0:12:32.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's not how you build a name.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:33.36,0:12:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}人们叫我们小偷
Dialogue: 2,0:12:33.36,0:12:34.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}People are calling us thieves.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:36.24,0:12:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所有这些案子... 我们必须全力以赴
Dialogue: 2,0:12:36.24,0:12:39.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All these cases... we have to fight against them all.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:40.32,0:12:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们必须与体制作斗争
Dialogue: 2,0:12:40.32,0:12:41.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have to fight against the system.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:42.24,0:12:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们必须洗清所有这些案子的嫌疑
Dialogue: 2,0:12:42.24,0:12:44.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We'll have to clear our names from all these cases.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:45.20,0:12:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}否则..
Dialogue: 2,0:12:45.20,0:12:46.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Or else...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:47.40,0:12:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}人们甚至不会放过我们的孩子
Dialogue: 2,0:12:47.40,0:12:50.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Forget us, people won't even leave our children in peace.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:53.44,0:12:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你觉得..
Dialogue: 2,0:12:53.44,0:12:54.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, do you think...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:55.52,0:12:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你可以读几本书，几天后成为一名律师？
Dialogue: 2,0:12:55.52,0:12:57.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...you'll read a few books, and become a lawyer in a couple of days?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:58.44,0:13:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你认为这些案子过几天就会结束吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:12:58.44,0:13:01.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you think, all these cases will be over in a couple of days?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:07.28,0:13:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我可以问你一些非正式的问题吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:07.28,0:13:08.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Can I ask you something off the records?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:15.24,0:13:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}已经三四年了... 我还在想..
Dialogue: 2,0:13:15.24,0:13:17.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's been three to four years... and I still wonder...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}到底是谁走漏了风声？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...who got this verbal diarrhoea?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:21.04,0:13:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[哈沙德]“你这个消息来源是谁? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:13:21.04,0:13:23.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Who turned this into a story? Who is this source?'
Dialogue: 3,0:13:25.08,0:13:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我从不透露我的消息来源，我认为这是不道德的
Dialogue: 2,0:13:25.08,0:13:27.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I never reveal my sources. I think it's unethical.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当然，我明白
Dialogue: 2,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Of course. I understand.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:30.84,0:13:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是现在这件事已经过去这么久了，又有什么关系呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:30.84,0:13:34.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But now this matter is old, it's stale. How does it matter?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:34.32,0:13:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那又怎样? 梅塔先生，我会把我的消息来源带进坟墓
Dialogue: 2,0:13:34.32,0:13:37.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So? Mr. Mehta, I take my sources to my grave.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:39.96,0:13:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我只是想弄明白..
Dialogue: 2,0:13:39.96,0:13:41.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm just trying to understand...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:41.36,0:13:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你的线人和我有私人恩怨
Dialogue: 2,0:13:41.36,0:13:44.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...if your source had a personal enmity with me.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他对我有意见吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Did he have a problem with me?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:47.20,0:13:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“啊? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:13:47.20,0:13:47.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Huh?'
Dialogue: 3,0:13:49.12,0:13:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每个人都在利用的系统的漏洞进行违规操作
Dialogue: 2,0:13:49.12,0:13:52.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The systemic loopholes and irregularities that everyone was exploiting...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:52.76,0:13:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}说他们是骗子
Dialogue: 2,0:13:52.76,0:13:54.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...calling them a scam...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:54.72,0:13:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也许他利用你来对付我？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:54.72,0:13:56.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...maybe he used you against me..?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:56.80,0:13:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}利用？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:56.80,0:13:57.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Use?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:58.12,0:14:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔先生，我的报告完全基于事实
Dialogue: 2,0:13:58.12,0:14:00.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr. Mehta, I report strictly based on facts.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:00.68,0:14:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我来这里是因为我认为有必要听听你对这件事的看法
Dialogue: 2,0:14:00.68,0:14:03.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm here because I think it's necessary to get your side of the story too.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:04.00,0:14:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[苏切塔]“因为我相信你也需要一个公平的听证会”
Dialogue: 2,0:14:04.00,0:14:05.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'Because I believe you need a fair hearing too.'
Dialogue: 3,0:14:07.80,0:14:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}公平的听证会？
Dialogue: 2,0:14:07.80,0:14:08.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Fair hearing?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:11.56,0:14:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的线人告诉了你一些事情..
Dialogue: 2,0:14:11.56,0:14:13.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Your source told you something then...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你相信了，并报道了出来
Dialogue: 2,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...you believed it and printed it.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:16.72,0:14:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在，当全世界都在指责我的时候..
Dialogue: 2,0:14:16.72,0:14:18.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And now, when the whole world is pointing fingers at me...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:19.48,0:14:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... ... 当我遇到麻烦的时候... ... 现在你又说什么公平听证会? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:14:19.48,0:14:21.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] '...when I'm in trouble... Now you talk about a fair hearing?'
Dialogue: 3,0:14:21.92,0:14:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我那时就想采访你，但你拒绝了
Dialogue: 2,0:14:21.92,0:14:24.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I tried talking to you even then. But you were in denial.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:24.92,0:14:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那时候，你可能觉得没有人可以碰你
Dialogue: 2,0:14:24.92,0:14:27.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Back then, you probably felt that no one can touch you.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:30.08,0:14:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你说的这些关于公平和不公平的事情
Dialogue: 2,0:14:30.08,0:14:32.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}These things you say... about being fair and unfair...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你以为我不明白你的意思吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...do you think I don't understand what you mean?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:36.40,0:14:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谈到一个人的利益，没有什么是公平或不公平的
Dialogue: 2,0:14:36.40,0:14:38.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}When it comes to one's gain, nothing is fair or unfair.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:41.68,0:14:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道，在商界，创造财富需要时机
Dialogue: 2,0:14:41.68,0:14:44.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You see, in business, it takes time to create fortune...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:44.80,0:14:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}毁灭财富也需要时机
Dialogue: 2,0:14:44.80,0:14:46.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and timing to kill it.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:47.64,0:14:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在你的新闻行业，这是一样的，不是吗? 这都是关于时机
Dialogue: 2,0:14:47.64,0:14:50.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In your business of journalism, it is the same, isn't it? It's all about timing.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你和你的线人时机掌握得很好
Dialogue: 2,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You and your source timed it very well.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:55.76,0:14:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔先生，我不是做新闻的
Dialogue: 2,0:14:55.76,0:14:58.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr. Mehta, I am not in the business of journalism.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:58.84,0:15:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我根据事实写报道
Dialogue: 2,0:14:58.84,0:15:00.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I write stories based on facts.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:00.80,0:15:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}重要的报道
Dialogue: 2,0:15:00.80,0:15:02.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Stories that are important. Stories that matter.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:02.68,0:15:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这对谁很重要？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:02.68,0:15:03.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Whom do they matter to?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:05.52,0:15:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}司法系统? 公众? 体制？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:05.52,0:15:08.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The judiciary? The public? The system?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:09.68,0:15:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这对任何人来说都不重要
Dialogue: 2,0:15:09.68,0:15:10.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It doesn't matter to anyone.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:11.12,0:15:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 没人在乎-我在乎
Dialogue: 2,0:15:11.12,0:15:13.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Nobody gives a f**k. - I give a f**k.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:13.48,0:15:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}由于这种明目张胆的误用和傲慢..
Dialogue: 2,0:15:13.48,0:15:15.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because of this blatant misuse and blatant arrogance...
Dialogue: 3,0:15:15.44,0:15:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}整个系统都是狗屁
Dialogue: 2,0:15:15.44,0:15:16.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the whole system is f****d.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:19.64,0:15:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你好像被冒犯了...-梅塔先生，我们没什么好说的了
Dialogue: 2,0:15:19.64,0:15:21.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- You seem offended... - Mr. Mehta, I think we are done.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:23.48,0:15:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我听说你在写一本关于这个”骗局”的书” ？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:23.48,0:15:26.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I hear, that you're writing a book on this "scam"?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:31.52,0:15:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}出版前一定要给我看看
Dialogue: 2,0:15:31.52,0:15:33.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do show it to me before you publish it.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:34.56,0:15:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我来交叉核对一下
Dialogue: 2,0:15:34.56,0:15:35.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll do a fact-check.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:46.92,0:15:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[德巴西]“终于! ”
Dialogue: 2,0:15:46.92,0:15:47.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Debashis] 'Finally!'
Dialogue: 3,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}完成了校对
Dialogue: 2,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Done with this proofreading.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:51.48,0:15:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有时候我觉得，我们应该采纳哈沙德的建议
Dialogue: 2,0:15:51.48,0:15:54.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sometimes I feel, we should've taken Harshad's suggestion.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:54.76,0:15:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他本可以帮忙的
Dialogue: 2,0:15:54.76,0:15:55.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He could've helped.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:56.44,0:15:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所有这些数字..
Dialogue: 2,0:15:56.44,0:15:59.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All these numbers and figures...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:00.24,0:16:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只是交叉核对一下，就会让人感到困惑
Dialogue: 2,0:16:00.24,0:16:03.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Just cross-checking them can leave one confused.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:03.96,0:16:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那我们还要在致谢中提到他的名字
Dialogue: 2,0:16:03.96,0:16:06.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And then, we would have to name him in the acknowledgements too.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:06.28,0:16:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哦，是的
Dialogue: 2,0:16:06.28,0:16:07.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:08.44,0:16:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 这提醒了我...-嗯..
Dialogue: 2,0:16:08.44,0:16:10.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- That reminds me... -[Sucheta] 'Hmm...'
Dialogue: 3,0:16:11.16,0:16:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们还要感谢卡拉姆昌德
Dialogue: 2,0:16:11.16,0:16:13.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We'll have to thank 'Karamchand' too.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:13.28,0:16:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你能不能别再叫我的线人“卡拉姆昌德”了？
Dialogue: 2,0:16:13.28,0:16:15.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Can you stop calling my source 'Karamchand'?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:15.24,0:16:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你知道我叫他 DT-哦，对，深喉
Dialogue: 2,0:16:15.24,0:16:18.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- You know I call him DT. - Oh, yes. Deep Throat. Yeah...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:19.84,0:16:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你本可以想出一些原创的东西
Dialogue: 2,0:16:19.84,0:16:21.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You could've come up with something original.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:22.28,0:16:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Debashis ]“你刚从《总统的手下》里偷来的”
Dialogue: 2,0:16:22.28,0:16:24.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Debashis] 'You just stole it from All the President's Men.'
Dialogue: 3,0:16:24.72,0:16:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你觉得这很有创意吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:16:24.72,0:16:26.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, you think that is original, huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:26.20,0:16:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}顺便告诉你，他们也获取了你的信息
Dialogue: 2,0:16:26.20,0:16:28.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They also stole it, for your information.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:28.44,0:16:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你什么都不知道，去做些调查吧
Dialogue: 2,0:16:28.44,0:16:30.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You don't know anything. Please go and do some research.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:30.48,0:16:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会的
Dialogue: 2,0:16:30.48,0:16:31.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I will.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:31.64,0:16:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我不需要给你的线人打电话
Dialogue: 2,0:16:31.64,0:16:34.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I don't need to call your source DT...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:35.24,0:16:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为我知道他的真名
Dialogue: 2,0:16:35.24,0:16:37.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...because I know his real name.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:39.72,0:16:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 真的?-当然
Dialogue: 2,0:16:39.72,0:16:41.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Really? - Of course.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:41.56,0:16:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你们两个见过几次面
Dialogue: 2,0:16:41.56,0:16:44.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A couple of meetings between you both...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:44.24,0:16:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我就知道”深喉”是谁了
Dialogue: 2,0:16:44.24,0:16:46.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and I had figured who this "Deep Throat" is...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:47.68,0:16:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 是的... 我知道...-你不相信我
Dialogue: 2,0:16:47.68,0:16:49.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Yeah... I know... -[Debashis] 'You don't believe me?'
Dialogue: 3,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有
Dialogue: 2,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:53.64,0:16:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我可以马上告诉你他的名字
Dialogue: 2,0:16:53.64,0:16:55.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I can tell you his name right away.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:57.44,0:16:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你能吗?-是的
Dialogue: 2,0:16:57.44,0:16:58.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Can you? - Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:00.96,0:17:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 告诉我-如果我告诉你呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:00.96,0:17:02.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Tell me. - What if I tell you?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:03.08,0:17:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 什么?-我能得到什么回报？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:03.08,0:17:04.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- What? - What do I get in return?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:04.88,0:17:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}回报? 你是个记者
Dialogue: 2,0:17:04.88,0:17:06.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Return? You're a journalist.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:06.84,0:17:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从什么时候开始记者开始考虑收益了？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:06.84,0:17:08.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Since when did the journalists start thinking about returns?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:08.52,0:17:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拜托! 总该有点奖励吧
Dialogue: 2,0:17:08.52,0:17:10.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come on! There has to be some reward.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:10.28,0:17:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}尽管我知道你消息来源的名字，但我一直对此保持沉默
Dialogue: 2,0:17:10.28,0:17:14.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I kept mum all this while in spite of knowing your source's name.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:15.68,0:17:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:17:15.68,0:17:17.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay. Fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:18.12,0:17:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你想要什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:18.12,0:17:19.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What do you want?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:21.60,0:17:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 用指甲花把你的手装饰好-Debu 拜托..
Dialogue: 2,0:17:21.60,0:17:24.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- With henna, keep your hands decorated - Debu, please...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}用鲜花，把轿子装饰起来
Dialogue: 2,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}With flowers, keep the palanquin decorated
Dialogue: 3,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}天啊 Debu
Dialogue: 2,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh, my God, Debu.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:28.32,0:17:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为了带你走，美丽的少女，你的爱人将踏上这段旅程！
Dialogue: 2,0:17:28.32,0:17:32.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}To take you away fair maiden, your beloved will make this journey!
Dialogue: 3,0:17:33.20,0:17:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你要干嘛？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:33.20,0:17:34.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Is there a point to this?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}死生契阔，与子成说执子之手，与子偕老
Dialogue: 2,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Marry me.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:45.92,0:17:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先告诉我消息来源的名字
Dialogue: 2,0:17:45.92,0:17:47.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tell me the name of my source, first.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:04.96,0:18:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的消息来源帮了大忙
Dialogue: 2,0:18:04.96,0:18:06.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Your source has helped so much.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:07.52,0:18:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们必须在书中感谢他，不是吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:18:07.52,0:18:09.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have to thank him in the book, don't we?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:54.40,0:18:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}36. Anil Khurana 先生
Dialogue: 2,0:18:54.40,0:18:56.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Number 36. Mr. Anil Khurana.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:58.44,0:18:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}下一辆车
Dialogue: 2,0:18:58.44,0:18:59.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Auctioneer] 'Next car.'
Dialogue: 3,0:19:08.24,0:19:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}20. Raja Duggal 先生
Dialogue: 2,0:19:08.24,0:19:10.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Number 20. Mr. Raja Duggal.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:36.56,0:19:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我作为首相的职责……
Dialogue: 2,0:19:36.56,0:19:39.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...My duties as Prime Minister...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:39.40,0:19:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}1996年，哈尔沙德再次走运
Dialogue: 2,0:19:39.40,0:19:42.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'In 1996, Harshad had a stroke of luck once again.'
Dialogue: 3,0:19:42.68,0:19:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拉奥总理辞去了总理职位
Dialogue: 2,0:19:42.68,0:19:45.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Prime Minister Rao was relinquishing his seat'.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:45.72,0:19:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德不再被视为政府的头号敌人... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:19:45.72,0:19:49.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Harshad was no longer perceived as government's enemy number one...'
Dialogue: 3,0:19:49.32,0:19:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“他在一些案件中也得到了和解”
Dialogue: 2,0:19:49.32,0:19:51.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'He had also got relief in a few cases.'
Dialogue: 3,0:19:52.24,0:19:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他的头脑又开始工作了
Dialogue: 2,0:19:52.24,0:19:53.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'His mind was at work again.'
Dialogue: 3,0:20:05.24,0:20:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}五年前我们扬言要摧毁美林
Dialogue: 2,0:20:05.24,0:20:07.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Five years ago we were to destroy Merill Lynch...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:09.80,0:20:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一路走来，我们却被摧毁了
Dialogue: 2,0:20:09.80,0:20:10.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Along the way, we got destroyed.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:13.00,0:20:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}72宗刑事案件
Dialogue: 2,0:20:13.00,0:20:14.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Seventy-two criminal cases.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:15.44,0:20:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有600多起民事案件
Dialogue: 2,0:20:15.44,0:20:17.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And more than 600 civil cases.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:18.88,0:20:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我比黑社会的老大指控还多
Dialogue: 2,0:20:18.88,0:20:20.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm bigger than a don of the underworld.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:21.84,0:20:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不过，是的... ... 这可能会让我进入吉尼斯世界纪录
Dialogue: 2,0:20:21.84,0:20:25.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'But yes... This might put me in the Guinness Book of World Records.'
Dialogue: 3,0:20:26.72,0:20:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别笑，这是事实，不是玩笑
Dialogue: 2,0:20:26.72,0:20:29.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't laugh. This is a fact. It's not a joke.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:31.20,0:20:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你真是太棒了
Dialogue: 2,0:20:31.20,0:20:32.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And you are amazing.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:33.08,0:20:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当我情况不好的时候
Dialogue: 2,0:20:33.08,0:20:34.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}When the going got tough...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:35.80,0:20:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嘿，白痴！
Dialogue: 2,0:20:35.80,0:20:36.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hey, idiot!
Dialogue: 3,0:20:37.52,0:20:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为你，中央调查局，IT... ... 他们使我的生活很悲惨
Dialogue: 2,0:20:37.52,0:20:41.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because of you, CBI, IT... ...they had made my life miserable.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:41.92,0:20:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我甚至不能安静地做爱
Dialogue: 2,0:20:41.92,0:20:43.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I wasn't allowed to even s**t in peace.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:45.16,0:20:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我知道如何保持低调”
Dialogue: 2,0:20:45.16,0:20:46.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Pranav] 'I know how to keep a low profile.'
Dialogue: 3,0:20:47.32,0:20:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就是为什么我很好，我很开心
Dialogue: 2,0:20:47.32,0:20:49.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That is why I'm fine. I'm happy.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:50.32,0:20:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是你..
Dialogue: 2,0:20:50.32,0:20:51.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But you...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:52.00,0:20:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你就是巴昌
Dialogue: 2,0:20:52.00,0:20:53.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You are Bachchan.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:55.48,0:20:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}新人已经进入了宝莱坞和市场
Dialogue: 2,0:20:55.48,0:20:57.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}New people have entered Bollywood and the market.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:59.56,0:21:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在，阿米塔布·巴沙坎和哈尔沙德 · 梅塔的时代已经结束了
Dialogue: 2,0:20:59.56,0:21:02.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now the era of both, Amitabh Bachchan and Harshad Mehta, is over.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:03.16,0:21:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}亲爱的..
Dialogue: 2,0:21:03.16,0:21:03.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Darling...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:05.00,0:21:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}时间不会白白流逝
Dialogue: 2,0:21:05.00,0:21:06.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...time doesn't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:06.72,0:21:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}相反，时间能给你经验
Dialogue: 2,0:21:06.72,0:21:08.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Rather, it brings with it. Experience.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:09.00,0:21:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}经验有它自己的价值，明白吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:21:09.00,0:21:11.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And experience has its own value. Get it?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:14.72,0:21:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没错，经验是有价值的
Dialogue: 2,0:21:14.72,0:21:16.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}True. Experience does have value.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:17.60,0:21:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就是我打算写一个报纸专栏的原因
Dialogue: 2,0:21:17.60,0:21:20.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's why I'm planning to write a newspaper column.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:20.92,0:21:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}关于市场
Dialogue: 2,0:21:20.92,0:21:21.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}About the market.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:23.40,0:21:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会告诉人们买什么，什么时候卖
Dialogue: 2,0:21:23.40,0:21:27.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What to buy, when to sell, I'll advise people.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:33.80,0:21:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}进来
Dialogue: 2,0:21:33.80,0:21:35.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[knock on the door] - Come in.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:43.64,0:21:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:21:43.64,0:21:44.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What is this?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:44.60,0:21:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是哈尔沙德 · 梅塔办公室发来的
Dialogue: 2,0:21:44.60,0:21:46.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Peon] 'This is from Harshad Mehta's office.'
Dialogue: 3,0:21:48.16,0:21:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}送货员说你会知道的
Dialogue: 2,0:21:48.16,0:21:51.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'The delivery boy said you'll know, that this is for you.'
Dialogue: 3,0:21:52.08,0:21:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 好的，谢谢-好的
Dialogue: 2,0:21:52.08,0:21:53.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Okay, thank you. -[Peon] 'Okay.'
Dialogue: 3,0:22:06.04,0:22:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 喂?-你拿到照片了吗，苏切塔？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:06.04,0:22:07.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Hello? - Did you get the photographs, Sucheta ji?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:08.44,0:22:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔先生，如果有关于你的文章..
Dialogue: 2,0:22:08.44,0:22:10.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr. Mehta, if there's an article about you...
Dialogue: 3,0:22:10.44,0:22:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我有很多你的照片
Dialogue: 2,0:22:10.44,0:22:11.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...then I have many pictures of you.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:11.80,0:22:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不知道你为什么要寄照片给我
Dialogue: 2,0:22:11.80,0:22:13.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't know why you're sending me all of this.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:13.52,0:22:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我怎么敢对我的老板指指点点呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:13.52,0:22:16.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How can I tell my boss what to do?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:16.56,0:22:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:16.56,0:22:17.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:17.64,0:22:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看起来好像没人告诉你
Dialogue: 2,0:22:17.64,0:22:19.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Looks like nobody has told you anything.'
Dialogue: 3,0:22:19.88,0:22:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧，我告诉你
Dialogue: 2,0:22:19.88,0:22:20.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Fine, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:21.72,0:22:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你将成为我的老板
Dialogue: 2,0:22:21.72,0:22:23.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You're going to be my boss.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:23.24,0:22:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[哈沙德]‘从下个月开始，我将在你们报纸上写一篇专栏文章’
Dialogue: 2,0:22:23.24,0:22:25.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'From next month, I am writing a column in your newspaper.'
Dialogue: 3,0:22:26.28,0:22:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}既然你是财经版的编辑
Dialogue: 2,0:22:26.28,0:22:28.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And since you're the editor of the finance section...
Dialogue: 3,0:22:28.72,0:22:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}’ ... 那你就是我的老板了，对吧? ’
Dialogue: 2,0:22:28.72,0:22:29.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...that makes you my boss, right?'
Dialogue: 3,0:22:30.52,0:22:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，我想，让我的老板选择
Dialogue: 2,0:22:30.52,0:22:32.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, I thought, let my boss select the photograph...
Dialogue: 3,0:22:33.08,0:22:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“专栏的照片..”
Dialogue: 2,0:22:33.08,0:22:34.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] '...that will go with the column.'
Dialogue: 3,0:22:38.12,0:22:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}(哈沙德)“我写这个专栏不是为了消磨时间”
Dialogue: 2,0:22:38.12,0:22:40.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'I'm not writing this column just to pass time.'
Dialogue: 3,0:22:41.72,0:22:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是一种保持在公众视野中的策略
Dialogue: 2,0:22:41.72,0:22:44.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is a strategy to remain in the public eye.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:46.08,0:22:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一个人们应该永远谈论的话题
Dialogue: 2,0:22:46.08,0:22:47.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}One should always remain a topic of conversation.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:50.28,0:22:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}欢迎，奈尔先生
Dialogue: 2,0:22:50.28,0:22:51.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Welcome, Mr. Nair.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:51.28,0:22:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 早上好-早上好
Dialogue: 2,0:22:51.28,0:22:52.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Hello, good morning. - Good morning.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:54.52,0:22:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 请坐-谢谢
Dialogue: 2,0:22:54.52,0:22:55.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Sit. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:57.20,0:22:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}阿什温，这是奈尔先生
Dialogue: 2,0:22:57.20,0:22:58.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ashwin, meet Mr. Nair.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:59.24,0:23:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}高级传媒经理
Dialogue: 2,0:22:59.24,0:23:00.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Senior media manager.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:00.88,0:23:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他在帮我申请《印度时报》的专栏
Dialogue: 2,0:23:00.88,0:23:02.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He's helping me get the column at Times of India.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:04.20,0:23:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}长官，有个问题
Dialogue: 2,0:23:04.20,0:23:05.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, there's a problem.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:05.60,0:23:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}高层对你的专栏有些意见
Dialogue: 2,0:23:05.60,0:23:07.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Top management has some issues with your column.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:08.28,0:23:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们不确定是否要马上出版
Dialogue: 2,0:23:08.28,0:23:10.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They are not sure whether they want to publish it right away or not.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:12.92,0:23:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是说苏切塔对我的专栏有意见
Dialogue: 2,0:23:12.92,0:23:15.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You mean Sucheta Dalal has a problem with my column.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:18.08,0:23:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是，先生，我们找到了一个解决办法
Dialogue: 2,0:23:18.08,0:23:19.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But sir, we've found a solution.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:19.92,0:23:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有一家印度报纸 Navdesh Samachar..
Dialogue: 2,0:23:19.92,0:23:22.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There's a Hindi newspaper Navdesh Samachar...
Dialogue: 3,0:23:22.84,0:23:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们准备出版你的专栏
Dialogue: 2,0:23:22.84,0:23:24.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...they are ready to publish your column.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:24.84,0:23:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[奈尔]“还能扩大投资者的影响范围”
Dialogue: 2,0:23:24.84,0:23:26.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Nair] 'It also has wider reach among your investors.'
Dialogue: 3,0:23:26.68,0:23:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“多数是散户”
Dialogue: 2,0:23:26.68,0:23:27.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Mostly, the smaller ones.'
Dialogue: 3,0:23:39.12,0:23:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“梅塔先生... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:23:39.12,0:23:40.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"Mr. Mehta..."
Dialogue: 3,0:23:40.60,0:23:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}” ... 有人说你的巅峰时期已经过去了... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:23:40.60,0:23:43.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...some people say that your best days are behind you..."
Dialogue: 3,0:23:44.64,0:23:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}” ... 而还有一些人仍然视你为市场领袖”
Dialogue: 2,0:23:44.64,0:23:47.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...while others look up at you as the market guru."
Dialogue: 3,0:23:48.84,0:23:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“这背后的秘密是什么? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:23:48.84,0:23:50.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"What is the secret behind this?"
Dialogue: 3,0:23:51.76,0:23:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“没有什么秘密”
Dialogue: 2,0:23:51.76,0:23:52.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"There is no secret."
Dialogue: 3,0:23:53.64,0:23:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“完全是实践经验”
Dialogue: 2,0:23:53.64,0:23:55.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"It's all about practical experiences."
Dialogue: 3,0:23:56.92,0:23:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我接触过多种业务”
Dialogue: 2,0:23:56.92,0:23:59.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"I've had this exposure of multiple businesses."
Dialogue: 3,0:24:00.04,0:24:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我很幸运，曾在股市工作过”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:00.04,0:24:03.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"And I am fortunate enough to have worked on the floors of stock market."
Dialogue: 3,0:24:04.96,0:24:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我曾涉足股票市场和货币市场”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:04.96,0:24:07.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"I have dabbled both in stock markets and money markets."
Dialogue: 3,0:24:08.32,0:24:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我敢肯定，没有哪个 MBA 或商界人士有过类似的经历”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:08.32,0:24:11.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"And I'm sure, no MBA or businessmen would have similar experience."
Dialogue: 3,0:24:12.68,0:24:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“所以，我的建议比书呆子的建议更实际”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:12.68,0:24:14.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"So, my advice are more practical than bookish."
Dialogue: 3,0:24:15.32,0:24:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“有人想要投资... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:15.32,0:24:17.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"Somebody wants to invest some money today..."
Dialogue: 3,0:24:18.84,0:24:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“他可以投资哪些股票... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:18.84,0:24:21.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"What would be the stocks he is likely to invest in..."
Dialogue: 3,0:24:21.56,0:24:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}” ... 或者说他应该投资哪些股? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:21.56,0:24:22.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...or he should invest in?"
Dialogue: 3,0:24:24.80,0:24:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“市场上有很多股票”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:24.80,0:24:26.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"There are lots of stocks."
Dialogue: 3,0:24:26.96,0:24:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我已经看中了其中的一些”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:26.96,0:24:28.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"I have identified a few of those."
Dialogue: 3,0:24:28.80,0:24:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“你愿意为我们指出其中的五支股吗? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:28.80,0:24:31.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"Would you like to identify five of them for us?"
Dialogue: 3,0:24:31.80,0:24:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“从长远来看会给投资者带来好处的 ”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:31.80,0:24:32.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"The five stocks..."
Dialogue: 3,0:24:32.88,0:24:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}” ...五只股票 ”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:32.88,0:24:36.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...that in the long term will yield dividends to its investors."
Dialogue: 3,0:24:36.40,0:24:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- ”你会怎么选? ”-”南迪先生... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:36.40,0:24:38.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- "Which would you choose?" - "Mr. Nandy..."
Dialogue: 3,0:24:39.04,0:24:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“你不能这么轻易地从我嘴里套出那些名字”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:39.04,0:24:41.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"You can't get those names out of me so easily."
Dialogue: 3,0:24:41.40,0:24:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“你必须为此付出代价”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:41.40,0:24:42.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] "You have to pay the price for it."
Dialogue: 3,0:24:43.24,0:24:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[电视评论员]“什么代价? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:43.24,0:24:44.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[TV Pundit] "And What is that price?"
Dialogue: 3,0:24:44.96,0:24:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“股票”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:44.96,0:24:45.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"The stock itself."
Dialogue: 3,0:24:49.00,0:24:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“听着，我知道很多人对我的预测感兴趣... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:49.00,0:24:51.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] "Look, I know many people are interested in my predictions..."
Dialogue: 3,0:24:51.32,0:24:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么也不做，却仍然看起来很忙
Dialogue: 2,0:24:51.32,0:24:53.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do nothing, and still look busy.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:53.16,0:24:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“所以，这就是我所做的”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:53.16,0:24:54.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] "So, here is what I've done."
Dialogue: 3,0:24:54.28,0:24:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就是他想做的一切
Dialogue: 2,0:24:54.28,0:24:55.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This all that he wants to do.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:55.60,0:24:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我们在互联网上创建了一个网站”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:55.60,0:24:57.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] "We have created a website on the internet."
Dialogue: 3,0:24:57.52,0:25:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 免费提供荐股服务-“ www.Harshad.com”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:57.52,0:25:00.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Doling out free advice. -[Harshad] "www.harshad.com"
Dialogue: 3,0:25:01.56,0:25:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我会随时更新... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:25:01.56,0:25:03.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad]"I'll keep you posted there..."
Dialogue: 3,0:25:03.68,0:25:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}(哈萨德)“ ... ... 关于投资的地点和时机”
Dialogue: 2,0:25:03.68,0:25:06.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad]"...about where to invest and when to invest."
Dialogue: 3,0:25:21.48,0:25:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，这些孩子是你的未来，对吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:25:21.48,0:25:23.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Dhananjay ji, these boys are your future, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:25:23.92,0:25:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的
Dialogue: 2,0:25:23.92,0:25:24.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:24.84,0:25:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}同样，这也是市场的未来
Dialogue: 2,0:25:24.84,0:25:26.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...in the same way, this is the market's future.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:27.84,0:25:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}至于情报，没有必要跑去交易所
Dialogue: 2,0:25:27.84,0:25:30.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now for tips, there's no need to go to the market and...
Dialogue: 3,0:25:30.12,0:25:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}喝不完的茶，吃不完的三明治
Dialogue: 2,0:25:30.12,0:25:32.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...have endless cups of tea and sandwiches.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:33.08,0:25:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有了这台电脑，你可以从家里得到情报，也可以交易
Dialogue: 2,0:25:33.08,0:25:36.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}With this computer, you can get tips and also trade, from home.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:37.48,0:25:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你明白了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:25:37.48,0:25:38.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Did you understand?
Dialogue: 3,0:25:39.16,0:25:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德兄弟
Dialogue: 2,0:25:39.16,0:25:40.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad Bhai...
Dialogue: 3,0:25:40.60,0:25:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的大脑里有望远镜吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:25:40.60,0:25:42.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...do you have a telescope attached to your brain?
Dialogue: 3,0:25:43.64,0:25:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“你怎么能预见未来? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:25:43.64,0:25:45.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Broker 1] 'How do you see so far into the future?'
Dialogue: 3,0:25:47.04,0:25:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}市场真的很想你
Dialogue: 2,0:25:47.04,0:25:48.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The market really misses you.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:49.76,0:25:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这次只要震撼市场就行了
Dialogue: 2,0:25:49.76,0:25:51.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Just rock the market this time.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:54.16,0:25:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，伙计，我见过最糟糕的情况
Dialogue: 2,0:25:54.16,0:25:55.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, buddy, I've seen the worst.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:57.12,0:25:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所有的账户都被冻结
Dialogue: 2,0:25:57.12,0:25:58.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All the accounts are suspended.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:59.72,0:26:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们不知道在这些案例中会有什么惊喜等着我们
Dialogue: 2,0:25:59.72,0:26:02.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We don't know what surprises are awaiting in these cases.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:04.56,0:26:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是我对未来有一些计划
Dialogue: 2,0:26:04.56,0:26:06.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I have some plans for the future.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:07.16,0:26:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德以高摩的名义做生意..
Dialogue: 2,0:26:07.16,0:26:10.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad Bhai, doing business in the name of Growmore...
Dialogue: 3,0:26:11.16,0:26:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的意思是，我们没有问题..
Dialogue: 2,0:26:11.16,0:26:12.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I mean, we have no problem...
Dialogue: 3,0:26:12.44,0:26:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不要误解我的意思，但是在市场上... 你知道..？
Dialogue: 2,0:26:12.44,0:26:15.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...Don't misunderstand me, but in the market... you know..?
Dialogue: 3,0:26:16.96,0:26:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们... 我们该怎么做？
Dialogue: 2,0:26:16.96,0:26:18.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How... how will we do it?
Dialogue: 3,0:26:20.12,0:26:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着伙计
Dialogue: 2,0:26:20.12,0:26:21.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, buddy.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:21.96,0:26:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}问题是名字，对吧? 所以我们要改名字
Dialogue: 2,0:26:21.96,0:26:24.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The problem is the name, right? So we'll change the name.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:25.48,0:26:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但前提是我们想要增长更多
Dialogue: 2,0:26:25.48,0:26:27.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But only if we want to grow more.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:33.60,0:26:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，购买 Videocon 的股票
Dialogue: 2,0:26:33.60,0:26:35.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Yes, buy the shares of Videocon.'
Dialogue: 3,0:26:35.84,0:26:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你可以在加尔各答买到
Dialogue: 2,0:26:35.84,0:26:37.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You can buy them from Calcutta.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:39.12,0:26:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“伙计，给它一点信心”
Dialogue: 2,0:26:39.12,0:26:40.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Buddy, give it some string.'
Dialogue: 3,0:26:41.20,0:26:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“方向正确”
Dialogue: 2,0:26:41.20,0:26:42.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'The wind is blowing in the right direction.'
Dialogue: 3,0:26:43.44,0:26:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这次会像风筝一样保持高度稳定
Dialogue: 2,0:26:43.44,0:26:45.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This needs to remain high like a kite. Steady.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:48.28,0:26:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好
Dialogue: 2,0:26:48.28,0:26:49.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:52.52,0:26:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}进来吧
Dialogue: 2,0:26:52.52,0:26:53.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come in.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:54.72,0:26:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么事，布尚？
Dialogue: 2,0:26:54.72,0:26:56.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you need something, Bhushan?
Dialogue: 3,0:26:56.96,0:26:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么? 我打扰你了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:26:56.96,0:26:58.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why? Did I disturb you?
Dialogue: 3,0:27:04.16,0:27:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我要和你谈谈
Dialogue: 2,0:27:04.16,0:27:05.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:06.20,0:27:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每个人都盯着我们
Dialogue: 2,0:27:06.20,0:27:08.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Everyone has a hawk's eye on us.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:12.20,0:27:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们已经交易很久了
Dialogue: 2,0:27:12.20,0:27:14.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We're trading after a long time.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:15.64,0:27:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在抬高 BPL 和 Sterlite 的股价
Dialogue: 2,0:27:15.64,0:27:18.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Bhushan] 'You're pushing up the prices of BPL and Sterlite.'
Dialogue: 3,0:27:19.96,0:27:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果有人怀疑..
Dialogue: 2,0:27:19.96,0:27:21.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If someone even suspects...
Dialogue: 3,0:27:26.40,0:27:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们犯了一个错误，对吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:27:26.40,0:27:27.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We had made a mistake, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:27:28.24,0:27:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因此，我正在从这些错误中吸取教训
Dialogue: 2,0:27:28.24,0:27:29.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'So, I'm moving forward learning from those mistakes.'
Dialogue: 3,0:27:32.00,0:27:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我只做我能承受的交易
Dialogue: 2,0:27:32.00,0:27:34.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I will only take it as high as I can handle.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:37.72,0:27:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是如果事情突然发生变化，我该怎么办？
Dialogue: 2,0:27:37.72,0:27:41.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But if something changes out of the blue, what can I do?
Dialogue: 3,0:27:46.68,0:27:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“15时45分，印度在Pokhran 范围内进行了... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:27:46.68,0:27:51.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"At 15:45 hours, India conducted..."
Dialogue: 3,0:27:51.40,0:27:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... 三次地下核试验”
Dialogue: 2,0:27:51.40,0:27:55.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...three underground nuclear tests in the Pokhran range."
Dialogue: 3,0:27:56.16,0:27:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[苏切塔]“在哈尔沙德的杠杆地位达到顶峰时... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:27:56.16,0:27:58.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'At the peak of Harshad's leveraged position...'
Dialogue: 3,0:27:58.08,0:28:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度在1998年6月进行了一次核试验
Dialogue: 2,0:27:58.08,0:28:01.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...India conducted a nuclear test in June 1998.'
Dialogue: 3,0:28:01.52,0:28:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}外国投资者惊慌失措，撤出资金，市场完全崩溃
Dialogue: 2,0:28:01.52,0:28:05.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Foreigners panicked, pulled out money and the market simply melted.'
Dialogue: 3,0:28:17.24,0:28:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 喂?-嗨
Dialogue: 2,0:28:17.24,0:28:18.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Hello? - Hi.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:18.68,0:28:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你还记得吗，我跟你说过股票的事..
Dialogue: 2,0:28:18.68,0:28:19.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you remember, I was telling you about the stocks...
Dialogue: 3,0:28:20.00,0:28:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 斯特莱特，BPL 和维多康，他们的价格是如何飙升的？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:20.00,0:28:22.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...of Sterlite, BPL and Videocon and how their prices were shooting up?
Dialogue: 3,0:28:23.08,0:28:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- [ DT ]‘ Hmm. ’-那么，他们所有的价格..
Dialogue: 2,0:28:23.08,0:28:24.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[DT] 'Hmm.' - So, all of their prices...
Dialogue: 3,0:28:24.64,0:28:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在市场下跌后大幅下跌
Dialogue: 2,0:28:24.64,0:28:26.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...drastically fell after the market sank.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:26.80,0:28:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ DT ]“我知道”
Dialogue: 2,0:28:26.80,0:28:27.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[DT] 'I know.'
Dialogue: 3,0:28:27.72,0:28:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，现在，有消息称是..
Dialogue: 2,0:28:27.72,0:28:28.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, now, the rumours are...
Dialogue: 3,0:28:28.72,0:28:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有一些 Damayanti 集团的公司..
Dialogue: 2,0:28:28.72,0:28:30.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that there are some Damayanti group of companies...
Dialogue: 3,0:28:30.84,0:28:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在操纵价格
Dialogue: 2,0:28:30.84,0:28:32.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that were rigging their prices.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:32.36,0:28:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在他们在交易所有一笔巨大的违约金
Dialogue: 2,0:28:32.36,0:28:34.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And now they have a huge payment default at BSE.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:34.24,0:28:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧，那又怎样
Dialogue: 2,0:28:34.24,0:28:35.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[DT] 'Okay, so?'
Dialogue: 3,0:28:35.56,0:28:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我发现不是强迫他们付钱
Dialogue: 2,0:28:35.56,0:28:38.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, I found out that instead of forcing them to pay up...
Dialogue: 3,0:28:38.60,0:28:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}交易所的人实际上是在帮助他们
Dialogue: 2,0:28:38.60,0:28:40.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the people at BSE are actually helping them.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:40.92,0:28:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的意思是，他们降低了控制的以股代息的利润
Dialogue: 2,0:28:40.92,0:28:43.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I mean, they've lowered the margins in the scrips they control...
Dialogue: 3,0:28:43.28,0:28:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}并且正在扭转其他公司以弥补其拖欠款项的情况
Dialogue: 2,0:28:43.28,0:28:46.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and they are arm-twisting other companies to cover their payment default.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:46.60,0:28:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}难以置信，为什么疯牛病会允许这样的事情发生？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:46.60,0:28:49.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Unbelievable. Why is BSE even allowing any of this?
Dialogue: 3,0:28:50.08,0:28:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对于一些闻所未闻的公司来说，这也是如此
Dialogue: 2,0:28:50.08,0:28:51.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That too, for some unheard-of company.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:51.96,0:28:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}跟我想的一模一样，所以我做了些调查
Dialogue: 2,0:28:51.96,0:28:54.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Exactly what I thought. So, I did some digging.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:55.04,0:28:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然而，看起来交易所正在接受我们的老朋友的指示
Dialogue: 2,0:28:55.04,0:28:57.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And, looks like BSE is taking instructions from our old friend.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:58.28,0:28:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁? 哈沙德？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:58.28,0:28:59.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who? Harshad?
Dialogue: 3,0:28:59.44,0:29:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有谁? 交易所有一半的人仍然是他的信徒
Dialogue: 2,0:28:59.44,0:29:02.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who else? Half the people at BSE are still his devotees.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:02.40,0:29:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们在半夜偷偷开市
Dialogue: 2,0:29:02.40,0:29:04.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They opened the trading system in the middle of the night...
Dialogue: 3,0:29:04.08,0:29:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}以与当天交易完全不符的价格
Dialogue: 2,0:29:04.08,0:29:05.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...to insert synchronised trades at prices...
Dialogue: 3,0:29:05.76,0:29:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}进行同步交易
Dialogue: 2,0:29:05.76,0:29:08.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that were completely out of line with the day's trading.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:08.64,0:29:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是为什么哈萨德要去拯救这个 Damayanti 集团？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:08.64,0:29:11.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But why is Harshad trying to bail out this Damayanti group?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:12.40,0:29:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不知道，哈沙德和高摩
Dialogue: 2,0:29:12.40,0:29:14.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't know. Harshad and Growmore...
Dialogue: 3,0:29:14.04,0:29:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}似乎和这些股票没有任何关系
Dialogue: 2,0:29:14.04,0:29:15.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...don't seem to have any connection to these stocks.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:15.76,0:29:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 除非-除非
Dialogue: 2,0:29:15.76,0:29:17.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Unless... - Unless...
Dialogue: 3,0:29:17.64,0:29:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Damayanti 集团和哈沙德有某种联系
Dialogue: 2,0:29:17.64,0:29:20.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...Damayanti Group is in some way connected to Harshad.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:20.32,0:29:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没错
Dialogue: 2,0:29:20.32,0:29:21.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Exactly.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:22.60,0:29:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你想让我做什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:22.60,0:29:23.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:23.60,0:29:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们要找出这个 Damayanti 集团的所有细节
Dialogue: 2,0:29:23.60,0:29:26.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have to pull out all the details of this Damayanti Group.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:26.32,0:29:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你能帮我吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:26.32,0:29:27.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Can you help me?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:28.88,0:29:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所有 Damayanti 集团的公司都是相同的注册地址
Dialogue: 2,0:29:28.88,0:29:31.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All the Damayanti Group of companies have the same address.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:31.68,0:29:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}1208 Maker Chambers 5，Nariman Point，400021.
Dialogue: 2,0:29:31.68,0:29:34.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's 1208 Maker Chambers 5, Nariman Point, 400021.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:35.08,0:29:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}高摩资产管理有限公司？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:35.08,0:29:36.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Growmore Research and Asset Management Limited?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:36.96,0:29:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没错
Dialogue: 2,0:29:36.96,0:29:38.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Thank you. Exactly.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:39.00,0:29:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而这四个人..
Dialogue: 2,0:29:39.00,0:29:40.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And these four people...
Dialogue: 3,0:29:40.16,0:29:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}迪利普 · 沙阿、维诺德 · 沙阿、阿尼尔 · 多希和迪尼什 · 多希
Dialogue: 2,0:29:40.16,0:29:42.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...Dilip Shah, Vinod Shah, Anil Doshi and Dinesh Doshi...
Dialogue: 3,0:29:42.96,0:29:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是这个 Damayanti 集团的董事
Dialogue: 2,0:29:42.96,0:29:44.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...are directors of this Damayanti group...
Dialogue: 3,0:29:44.48,0:29:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}各种各样的排列组合
Dialogue: 2,0:29:44.48,0:29:46.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...in various permutations and combinations.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:46.28,0:29:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:29:46.28,0:29:46.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay...
Dialogue: 3,0:29:46.84,0:29:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道他们是谁吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:46.84,0:29:47.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you know who they are?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:48.48,0:29:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}乔蒂 · 梅塔的兄弟们
Dialogue: 2,0:29:48.48,0:29:50.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Jyoti Mehta's brothers.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:50.64,0:29:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}乔蒂是哈沙德的妻子？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:50.64,0:29:51.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Jyoti is Harshad's wife?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:53.96,0:29:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个歹徒以他岳父岳母的名义开办了一家公司
Dialogue: 2,0:29:53.96,0:29:56.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The outlaw has started a company in the name of his in-laws.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:56.32,0:30:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没错，我们终于有证据证明哈沙德和 Damayanti 集团有关
Dialogue: 2,0:29:56.32,0:30:00.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Exactly. We finally have evidence linking Harshad to Damayanti.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:00.20,0:30:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么样？
Dialogue: 2,0:30:00.20,0:30:01.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You know what?
Dialogue: 3,0:30:01.68,0:30:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我们把这些都交给 SEBI
Dialogue: 2,0:30:01.68,0:30:03.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let's just give all of this to SEBI.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:03.80,0:30:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}与上次不同，这次不再是纸老虎
Dialogue: 2,0:30:03.80,0:30:06.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Unlike last time, they are no longer toothless tigers.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:06.00,0:30:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们有证据
Dialogue: 2,0:30:06.00,0:30:07.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They have all the powers.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:07.92,0:30:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让他们去调查吧
Dialogue: 2,0:30:07.92,0:30:09.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let them investigate.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:11.12,0:30:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好
Dialogue: 2,0:30:11.12,0:30:11.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:27.44,0:30:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}2月27日，谁从孟买来到了德里？
Dialogue: 2,0:30:27.44,0:30:29.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who had travelled from Mumbai to Delhi on 27th February?
Dialogue: 3,0:30:30.08,0:30:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德 · 梅塔？
Dialogue: 2,0:30:30.08,0:30:30.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad Mehta?
Dialogue: 3,0:30:31.48,0:30:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不，先生，是我们的一个员工
Dialogue: 2,0:30:31.48,0:30:33.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Accountant] 'No, sir. It was one of our employees.'
Dialogue: 3,0:30:33.72,0:30:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你看，票是用他的名字订的
Dialogue: 2,0:30:33.72,0:30:35.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, the ticket has been booked in his name.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:36.08,0:30:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}打电话给航空公司确认一下..
Dialogue: 2,0:30:36.08,0:30:37.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Just call up the airline and confirm...
Dialogue: 3,0:30:37.52,0:30:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德 · 梅塔是不是在这一天去了德里
Dialogue: 2,0:30:37.52,0:30:39.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...if Harshad Mehta travelled to Delhi on this date.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:39.48,0:30:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好的，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:30:39.48,0:30:40.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sure, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:40.04,0:30:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个号码接到了很多电话
Dialogue: 2,0:30:40.04,0:30:41.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[SEBI Official 2] 'Many calls have been made to this number.'
Dialogue: 3,0:30:41.92,0:30:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而且，很多是从同一个号码打来的
Dialogue: 2,0:30:41.92,0:30:43.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And, many calls have also been received from the same number.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:44.56,0:30:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 这是谁的号码?-先生，我不知道
Dialogue: 2,0:30:44.56,0:30:48.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Whose number is this? - Sir, I don't know.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:49.36,0:30:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，这是所有的合同条款
Dialogue: 2,0:30:49.36,0:30:51.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, here are all the contract notes.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:51.16,0:30:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}BPL，录像机，小心保管资料
Dialogue: 2,0:30:51.16,0:30:54.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}BPL, Videocon, Sterlite. Keep it carefully.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:54.04,0:30:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好的，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:30:54.04,0:30:54.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sure, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:58.88,0:31:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Sucheta ]“ Damayanti 集团是由哈尔沙德建立的，这是公认的事实”
Dialogue: 2,0:30:58.88,0:31:02.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'It was established that Damayanti Group was set up by Harshad.'
Dialogue: 3,0:31:02.84,0:31:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}甚至没有人试图掩盖他们的踪迹
Dialogue: 2,0:31:02.84,0:31:05.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'No one even tried to cover their tracks.'
Dialogue: 3,0:31:05.64,0:31:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}通过垄断股票和操纵价格... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:31:05.64,0:31:08.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'By cornering of shares and price manipulation...'
Dialogue: 3,0:31:08.64,0:31:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们创造了一个人工市场，最终却崩溃了
Dialogue: 2,0:31:08.64,0:31:13.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...they created an artificial market which ultimately crashed.'
Dialogue: 3,0:31:27.92,0:31:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你怎么还没准备好？
Dialogue: 2,0:31:27.92,0:31:29.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How come you aren't ready yet?
Dialogue: 3,0:31:30.28,0:31:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你今天不是要去拿你的电视录像吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:31:30.28,0:31:32.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't you have to go for your TV recording today?
Dialogue: 3,0:31:41.20,0:31:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}最近几天不会有录音
Dialogue: 2,0:31:41.20,0:31:42.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There won't be any recording for a few days.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:44.84,0:31:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}发生了这么多事情... 看起来不妙..
Dialogue: 2,0:31:44.84,0:31:48.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}With all the things going on... It won't look good...
Dialogue: 3,0:31:49.96,0:31:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没关系
Dialogue: 2,0:31:49.96,0:31:51.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That is fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:52.08,0:31:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是你今天甚至都没有锻炼
Dialogue: 2,0:31:52.08,0:31:53.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But you didn't even exercise today.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:55.12,0:31:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}医生建议你每天锻炼身体
Dialogue: 2,0:31:55.12,0:31:57.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The doctor has advised you to exercise every day.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:58.80,0:31:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:31:58.80,0:31:59.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then?
Dialogue: 3,0:32:01.40,0:32:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来吧
Dialogue: 2,0:32:01.40,0:32:02.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come on.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:03.00,0:32:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}跑一会儿
Dialogue: 2,0:32:03.00,0:32:03.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Run a little.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:07.12,0:32:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我已经跑了很多年了
Dialogue: 2,0:32:07.12,0:32:08.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I've been running for years now.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:11.72,0:32:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在仍然在跑
Dialogue: 2,0:32:11.72,0:32:12.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, I'm still running.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:17.16,0:32:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我累了
Dialogue: 2,0:32:17.16,0:32:18.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm tired now.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:23.28,0:32:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只想休息
Dialogue: 2,0:32:23.28,0:32:24.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I just want to rest now.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:26.24,0:32:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我需要平静
Dialogue: 2,0:32:26.24,0:32:27.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I need some peace.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:32.92,0:32:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想要平静，首先让头脑冷静
Dialogue: 2,0:32:32.92,0:32:35.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}For peace, you need to first calm your mind.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:37.64,0:32:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你想得太多了
Dialogue: 2,0:32:37.64,0:32:38.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You think too much.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:40.24,0:32:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}停止思考
Dialogue: 2,0:32:40.24,0:32:41.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Stop thinking.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:42.12,0:32:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一切都会好起来的
Dialogue: 2,0:32:42.12,0:32:43.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then everything will be fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:45.88,0:32:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有..
Dialogue: 2,0:32:45.88,0:32:46.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And...
Dialogue: 3,0:32:47.48,0:32:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}顺便说一句
Dialogue: 2,0:32:47.48,0:32:48.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}By the way...
Dialogue: 3,0:32:49.04,0:32:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你想要平静，你可以一直想着我
Dialogue: 2,0:32:49.04,0:32:52.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...if you want peace, you can always think about me.
Dialogue: 3,0:33:01.52,0:33:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧，我试试
Dialogue: 2,0:33:01.52,0:33:03.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay, let's try that.
Dialogue: 3,0:33:07.20,0:33:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不管怎样..
Dialogue: 2,0:33:07.20,0:33:08.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Anyway...
Dialogue: 3,0:33:09.56,0:33:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我现在无处可去
Dialogue: 2,0:33:09.56,0:33:10.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have nowhere to go now.
Dialogue: 3,0:33:11.44,0:33:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没必要去任何地方，留在这里... 和我在一起
Dialogue: 2,0:33:11.44,0:33:15.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There's no need to go anywhere. Stay here... with me.
Dialogue: 3,0:33:23.68,0:33:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我可能时日无多了
Dialogue: 2,0:33:23.68,0:33:25.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}My time might be up, anytime now.
Dialogue: 3,0:33:27.48,0:33:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我可能不得不去... ... 很快... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:33:27.48,0:33:29.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'And I might have to go... soon...'
Dialogue: 3,0:33:29.08,0:33:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你为什么说这些可怕的倒霉话？
Dialogue: 2,0:33:29.08,0:33:30.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why are you saying such scary jinxed things?
Dialogue: 3,0:33:33.04,0:33:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你还跟别人说要永远保持积极的态度
Dialogue: 2,0:33:33.04,0:33:35.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You advise everyone else to always think positive.
Dialogue: 3,0:33:38.92,0:33:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我开玩笑的
Dialogue: 2,0:33:38.92,0:33:40.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm just joking.
Dialogue: 3,0:33:42.76,0:33:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看着我..
Dialogue: 2,0:33:42.76,0:33:43.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look at me...
Dialogue: 3,0:33:44.84,0:33:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会怎么样？
Dialogue: 2,0:33:44.84,0:33:46.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What's going to happen to me?
Dialogue: 3,0:33:50.52,0:33:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-给我泡点茶-不，我不去
Dialogue: 2,0:33:50.52,0:33:53.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Come on, make some tea for me. - No, I won't.
Dialogue: 3,0:33:54.60,0:33:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在我出事之前赶快泡点茶
Dialogue: 2,0:33:54.60,0:33:57.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Quickly make some tea before something happens to me.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:02.36,0:34:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不会丢下你一个人的
Dialogue: 2,0:34:02.36,0:34:03.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm not leaving you alone.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:09.52,0:34:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你穿戴整齐，好像今天要录节目似的
Dialogue: 2,0:34:09.52,0:34:12.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You're all dressed up, as if you were going to be recorded today.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:14.16,0:34:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好看吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:34:14.16,0:34:15.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Is it nice?
Dialogue: 3,0:34:46.60,0:34:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}‘布尚? ’
Dialogue: 2,0:34:46.60,0:34:47.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ashwin] 'Bhushan?'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:48.48,0:34:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你要走了吗?-是的，我没什么工作，所以..
Dialogue: 2,0:34:48.48,0:34:51.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Are you leaving? - Yes. I didn't have much work, so...
Dialogue: 3,0:34:51.96,0:34:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么? 发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 2,0:34:51.96,0:34:52.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why? What happened?
Dialogue: 3,0:34:53.44,0:34:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}管理员已经把报告送来了
Dialogue: 2,0:34:53.44,0:34:54.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The custodian has sent the report.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:55.36,0:34:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 报告?-是的
Dialogue: 2,0:34:55.36,0:34:56.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Report? - Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:57.40,0:34:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那个定期的..
Dialogue: 2,0:34:57.40,0:34:58.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The one which comes periodically...
Dialogue: 3,0:34:59.68,0:35:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- ... 关于负债和资产的报告?-哦... 是的..
Dialogue: 2,0:34:59.68,0:35:01.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- ...about liabilities and assets? - Oh... Yes...
Dialogue: 3,0:35:03.60,0:35:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有很多股票都不见了
Dialogue: 2,0:35:03.60,0:35:05.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}An entire lot of shares is missing, Bhushan.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:06.96,0:35:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我这里有记录，但不在他们的报告里
Dialogue: 2,0:35:06.96,0:35:09.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I mean, it's in my records but not in their reports.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:10.32,0:35:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们一定是在审计的时候漏掉了
Dialogue: 2,0:35:10.32,0:35:12.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They must've messed it up during the audit.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:12.36,0:35:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我再看看那些报告
Dialogue: 2,0:35:12.36,0:35:13.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll look into those reports again.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:14.32,0:35:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}将近270万股股票不见了
Dialogue: 2,0:35:14.32,0:35:16.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Almost 27 lakh shares are missing.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:17.20,0:35:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}大约价值30亿卢比
Dialogue: 2,0:35:17.20,0:35:18.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Approximately worth 300 crores.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:20.68,0:35:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你看
Dialogue: 2,0:35:20.68,0:35:21.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Here...
Dialogue: 3,0:35:22.60,0:35:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看看这个..
Dialogue: 2,0:35:22.60,0:35:23.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look at this...
Dialogue: 3,0:35:24.20,0:35:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你以前有没有遇到过这个错误？
Dialogue: 2,0:35:24.20,0:35:25.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Did you come across this mistake before?
Dialogue: 3,0:35:27.16,0:35:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}兄弟，你们有有价值200亿的资产..
Dialogue: 2,0:35:27.16,0:35:29.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ashwin Bhai, there are assets worth 2,000 crores...
Dialogue: 3,0:35:29.20,0:35:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有价值1600亿卢比的债务
Dialogue: 2,0:35:29.20,0:35:31.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and liabilities worth 16,000 crores.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:31.24,0:35:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}天知道，有多少公司的股票
Dialogue: 2,0:35:31.24,0:35:33.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And god knows, how many shares of how many companies.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:34.36,0:35:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}光是保存记录就让我头脑发热
Dialogue: 2,0:35:34.36,0:35:36.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Just maintaining the records curdles my brain.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:37.24,0:35:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你也看到了他们是怎样把股份存放在储藏室里的
Dialogue: 2,0:35:37.24,0:35:40.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And you have seen how they keep the shares in the custodian's storeroom.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:42.80,0:35:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我希望他们没有弄丢那些股票
Dialogue: 2,0:35:42.80,0:35:45.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I hope they haven't misplaced those shares.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:45.12,0:35:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}放错地方了？
Dialogue: 2,0:35:45.12,0:35:46.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Misplace?
Dialogue: 3,0:35:46.68,0:35:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不过别担心，阿什温大哥，我会再查一遍所有的记录
Dialogue: 2,0:35:46.68,0:35:49.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But don't worry, Ashwin Bhai. I'll check all the records again.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:52.60,0:35:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我可以走了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:35:52.60,0:35:53.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}May I go?
Dialogue: 3,0:35:55.04,0:35:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你赶时间吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:35:55.04,0:35:55.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you in a hurry?
Dialogue: 3,0:35:56.40,0:35:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不... 你需要的话我就留下来
Dialogue: 2,0:35:56.40,0:35:58.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No... We'll leave together if you say.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:01.16,0:36:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}去吧
Dialogue: 2,0:36:01.16,0:36:02.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Go.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:03.56,0:36:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}再见
Dialogue: 2,0:36:03.56,0:36:04.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}See you.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:06.12,0:36:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“270万股股票怎么会从记录中消失? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:36:06.12,0:36:08.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'How can 27 lakh shares go missing from the records?'
Dialogue: 3,0:36:09.60,0:36:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你的数字从来没有错过-没错
Dialogue: 2,0:36:09.60,0:36:11.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Your figures are never wrong. - No, they aren't.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:13.24,0:36:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是你知道，布尚保存着所有资产的记录
Dialogue: 2,0:36:13.24,0:36:16.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But you know. Bhushan maintains the records of all the assets.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:17.04,0:36:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他负责检查管理员的所有报告
Dialogue: 2,0:36:17.04,0:36:19.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He is the one who checks all the reports of the custodian.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:19.84,0:36:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我认为，随着年龄的增长，他脑子已经不太好使了
Dialogue: 2,0:36:19.84,0:36:23.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I think, with age, his brain has stopped working.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:24.84,0:36:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我不知道他在想什么”
Dialogue: 2,0:36:24.84,0:36:26.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ashwin] 'I don't know what goes on his mind.'
Dialogue: 3,0:36:26.76,0:36:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谢天谢地，我检查了旧的记录，发现了这个错误
Dialogue: 2,0:36:26.76,0:36:30.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Thankfully, I checked the old records and spotted this mistake.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:31.48,0:36:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}兄弟，我们必须尽快通知托管人
Dialogue: 2,0:36:31.48,0:36:35.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bhai, we must inform the custodian as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:35.44,0:36:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不，等等..
Dialogue: 2,0:36:35.44,0:36:36.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, wait...
Dialogue: 3,0:36:37.92,0:36:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那个疯子
Dialogue: 2,0:36:37.92,0:36:38.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He's crazy.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:39.84,0:36:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他反而会怀疑我们
Dialogue: 2,0:36:39.84,0:36:40.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He'll suspect us instead.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:43.32,0:36:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们再问问布尚，让他再检查一遍
Dialogue: 2,0:36:43.32,0:36:44.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let's ask Bhushan. Let him check them again.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:45.28,0:36:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}兄弟，你们不懂法律
Dialogue: 2,0:36:45.28,0:36:48.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bhai, Bhushan and you don't understand the law.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:48.80,0:36:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在监护人之前的报告中
Dialogue: 2,0:36:48.80,0:36:51.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In none of the previous reports from the custodian...
Dialogue: 3,0:36:51.24,0:36:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有这些股票的记录
Dialogue: 2,0:36:51.24,0:36:52.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...are these shares mentioned.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:52.24,0:36:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是，他们在我们的记录中有
Dialogue: 2,0:36:52.24,0:36:53.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But, they're showing in our records.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:53.92,0:36:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我亲自检查过了
Dialogue: 2,0:36:53.92,0:36:55.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I've checked them myself.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:57.20,0:37:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我觉得是92年
Dialogue: 2,0:36:57.20,0:37:00.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I feel, in '92, when we were both in custody...
Dialogue: 3,0:37:00.44,0:37:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们都被拘留的时候就搞错了
Dialogue: 2,0:37:00.44,0:37:01.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that's when this mistake has occurred in the records.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:04.00,0:37:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[阿什温]“我觉得我们应该明天去，然后汇报一下情况”
Dialogue: 2,0:37:04.00,0:37:05.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ashwin] 'I feel we should go tomorrow, and complain about this.'
Dialogue: 3,0:37:06.64,0:37:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}30亿，兄弟
Dialogue: 2,0:37:06.64,0:37:08.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's 300 crores, Bhai.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:08.44,0:37:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我们不早点去找他
Dialogue: 2,0:37:08.44,0:37:10.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If we delay even a little...
Dialogue: 3,0:37:10.68,0:37:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}即使可能是他们审计过程中出现的错误
Dialogue: 2,0:37:10.68,0:37:13.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the custodian might blame this back on us.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:13.76,0:37:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}管理员还是可能会把责任推到我们身上
Dialogue: 2,0:37:13.76,0:37:16.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ashwin] 'Even if the problem might be in their records.'
Dialogue: 3,0:37:17.20,0:37:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我们能找到这270万股..
Dialogue: 2,0:37:17.20,0:37:19.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If we find these 27 lakh shares...
Dialogue: 3,0:37:19.44,0:37:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们的债务将减少30亿卢比
Dialogue: 2,0:37:19.44,0:37:21.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...our liability will be reduced by 300 crores.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:24.52,0:37:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 30亿卢比?-是的
Dialogue: 2,0:37:24.52,0:37:26.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Three hundred crores? -[Ashwin] 'Yes.'
Dialogue: 3,0:37:29.08,0:37:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:37:29.08,0:37:29.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:31.32,0:37:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-说吧-我们只有一个请求
Dialogue: 2,0:37:31.32,0:37:33.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Tell me. - We have just one request.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:34.20,0:37:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}请找出所有这些股票..
Dialogue: 2,0:37:34.20,0:37:36.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Please locate all these shares...
Dialogue: 3,0:37:36.56,0:37:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 以我们的名义恢复它们，还有所有的利润
Dialogue: 2,0:37:36.56,0:37:39.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and restore them in our names, with all the benefits.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:39.96,0:37:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}首先告诉我，我们谈论的是哪些股票？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:39.96,0:37:42.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}First tell me, which shares are we talking about?
Dialogue: 3,0:37:43.40,0:37:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们是怎么消失的？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:43.40,0:37:44.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And how did they go missing?
Dialogue: 3,0:37:46.12,0:37:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在1992年，这个案子中..
Dialogue: 2,0:37:46.12,0:37:47.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In 1992, during the case...
Dialogue: 3,0:37:49.16,0:37:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}法庭扣押了我们所有的财产
Dialogue: 2,0:37:49.16,0:37:51.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the court had attached all our assets.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:52.24,0:37:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有两到三间储藏室，里面装满了股票
Dialogue: 2,0:37:52.24,0:37:54.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There were two to three storerooms full of shares.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:55.04,0:37:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}其中有270万股
Dialogue: 2,0:37:55.04,0:37:56.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And among them, were these 27 lakh shares.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:57.52,0:37:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}两到三间储藏室？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:57.52,0:37:59.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Two to three storerooms?
Dialogue: 3,0:38:03.40,0:38:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}两三个装满股票的储藏室怎么会被托管人弄丢呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:38:03.40,0:38:06.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How can two-three storerooms full of shares be misplaced by the custodian?
Dialogue: 3,0:38:08.04,0:38:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你想说什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:38:08.04,0:38:09.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 3,0:38:10.08,0:38:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们偷走了自己的股份？
Dialogue: 2,0:38:10.08,0:38:11.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That we've stolen our own attached shares?
Dialogue: 3,0:38:12.24,0:38:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你是这个意思，对吧?-请冷静
Dialogue: 2,0:38:12.24,0:38:14.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- That's what you mean, right? -[Custodian] 'Please calm down.'
Dialogue: 3,0:38:16.68,0:38:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们会调查的
Dialogue: 2,0:38:16.68,0:38:18.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We'll do an investigation.
Dialogue: 3,0:38:19.08,0:38:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}无论如何，你的记录是独一无二的
Dialogue: 2,0:38:19.08,0:38:21.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Your record is unique, anyway.'
Dialogue: 3,0:38:21.84,0:38:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}正在进行很多同步调查
Dialogue: 2,0:38:21.84,0:38:23.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There are so many on-going investigations.
Dialogue: 3,0:38:23.68,0:38:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}再多一项又如何？
Dialogue: 2,0:38:23.68,0:38:24.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What's one more?
Dialogue: 3,0:38:39.08,0:38:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么了，兄弟？
Dialogue: 2,0:38:39.08,0:38:40.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What is it, Bhai?
Dialogue: 3,0:38:42.44,0:38:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你又做了什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:38:42.44,0:38:43.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What have you done now?
Dialogue: 3,0:38:45.84,0:38:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们做了什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:38:45.84,0:38:46.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What did we do?
Dialogue: 3,0:38:47.68,0:38:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么中央调查局要审问我？
Dialogue: 2,0:38:47.68,0:38:49.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why does the CBI want to interrogate me?
Dialogue: 3,0:38:50.40,0:38:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们为什么又打电话给我？
Dialogue: 2,0:38:50.40,0:38:51.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why did they call me again?
Dialogue: 3,0:38:52.96,0:38:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没什么，冷静点
Dialogue: 2,0:38:52.96,0:38:54.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's nothing. Calm down.
Dialogue: 3,0:38:57.76,0:39:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们和托管人谈了丢失股票的事
Dialogue: 2,0:38:57.76,0:39:00.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We spoke to the custodian about those missing shares.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:01.68,0:39:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}肯定是有警察和调查局的人说了
Dialogue: 2,0:39:01.68,0:39:03.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That a*****e must've told the CBI.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:04.84,0:39:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[哈沙德]“所以现在，中央调查局正在进行调查”
Dialogue: 2,0:39:04.84,0:39:06.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'So now, CBI is enquiring.'
Dialogue: 3,0:39:07.08,0:39:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}或者是在假装询问
Dialogue: 2,0:39:07.08,0:39:08.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Or they are pretending to enquire.'
Dialogue: 3,0:39:10.36,0:39:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 2,0:39:10.36,0:39:11.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:11.24,0:39:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们会询问一些员工仅此而已
Dialogue: 2,0:39:11.24,0:39:13.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They'll question a few employees. That's it.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:13.56,0:39:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就这样？
Dialogue: 2,0:39:13.56,0:39:14.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's it?
Dialogue: 3,0:39:15.76,0:39:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你去找管理员之前应该先跟我说一声
Dialogue: 2,0:39:15.76,0:39:18.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You should've spoken to me before going to the custodian.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:19.44,0:39:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“跟你说一声? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:39:19.44,0:39:20.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ashwin] 'Spoken to you?'
Dialogue: 3,0:39:21.76,0:39:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么意思？
Dialogue: 2,0:39:21.76,0:39:22.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Meaning?
Dialogue: 3,0:39:22.60,0:39:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}阿什温兄弟，如果 CBI 找我麻烦那么..
Dialogue: 2,0:39:22.60,0:39:25.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ashwin Bhai, if CBI troubles me, then...
Dialogue: 3,0:39:25.24,0:39:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“嘿! ”
Dialogue: 2,0:39:25.24,0:39:26.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Hey!'
Dialogue: 3,0:39:27.24,0:39:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}坐下来，冷静点
Dialogue: 2,0:39:27.24,0:39:28.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sit down and speak calmly.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:32.52,0:39:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 坐下!-我不想坐！
Dialogue: 2,0:39:32.52,0:39:34.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Sit! - I don't want to sit!
Dialogue: 3,0:39:37.28,0:39:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那就说吧
Dialogue: 2,0:39:37.28,0:39:38.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then talk.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:39.96,0:39:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}股票没丢
Dialogue: 2,0:39:39.96,0:39:41.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The shares aren't missing.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:43.16,0:39:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“你是什么意思? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:39:43.16,0:39:43.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'What do you mean?'
Dialogue: 3,0:39:45.00,0:39:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我卖掉了那些股票
Dialogue: 2,0:39:45.00,0:39:46.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I sold those shares.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:51.84,0:39:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你把它们卖了！
Dialogue: 2,0:39:51.84,0:39:52.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You sold them!
Dialogue: 3,0:39:54.68,0:39:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这些股份是法院附加的财产
Dialogue: 2,0:39:54.68,0:39:56.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Those shares were attached by the court.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:57.72,0:39:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么叫你把它们卖了
Dialogue: 2,0:39:57.72,0:39:58.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ashwin] 'What do you mean you sold them?'
Dialogue: 3,0:40:00.72,0:40:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你把脑子也卖了吗? ！
Dialogue: 2,0:40:00.72,0:40:02.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Have you sold your brain too?!
Dialogue: 3,0:40:02.88,0:40:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}法院从来没有附加这些股份
Dialogue: 2,0:40:02.88,0:40:05.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The court never attached those shares.
Dialogue: 3,0:40:06.12,0:40:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当我出具资产清单时，我根本没有包括这些股票
Dialogue: 2,0:40:06.12,0:40:09.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}When I gave the list of assets, I didn't include those shares at all.
Dialogue: 3,0:40:11.52,0:40:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后就像我们经常做的那样，我转移了所有的股份..
Dialogue: 2,0:40:11.52,0:40:15.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then as we have often done, I transferred all those shares...
Dialogue: 3,0:40:15.72,0:40:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}卖给一家幌子公司，然后在市场上卖掉
Dialogue: 2,0:40:15.72,0:40:18.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...to a front company and sold them off at the open market.
Dialogue: 3,0:40:18.72,0:40:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}混蛋！
Dialogue: 2,0:40:18.72,0:40:19.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A*****e!
Dialogue: 3,0:40:37.92,0:40:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是你爹的股份吗！
Dialogue: 2,0:40:37.92,0:40:39.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Were they your father's shares, m**********r!
Dialogue: 3,0:40:46.16,0:40:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你怎么能这样对待我们？
Dialogue: 2,0:40:46.16,0:40:48.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How can you f**k us over being one of us?
Dialogue: 3,0:40:49.32,0:40:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Bhushan ]“我... ? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:40:49.32,0:40:50.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Bhushan] 'I..?'
Dialogue: 3,0:40:51.12,0:40:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我这样对待你们? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:40:51.12,0:40:52.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'I f****d you over?'
Dialogue: 3,0:40:52.84,0:40:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我他妈这样对待你们? ! ”
Dialogue: 2,0:40:52.84,0:40:54.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'I f****d you over?!'
Dialogue: 3,0:40:55.76,0:40:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我他妈的一直在贴你的冷屁股！
Dialogue: 2,0:40:55.76,0:40:59.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All this while I've been kissing your a**!
Dialogue: 3,0:41:01.52,0:41:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}中央调查局的人在我脸上撒尿的时候，你做什么了？
Dialogue: 2,0:41:01.52,0:41:04.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}CBI was pissing on my face. What did you expect me to do?
Dialogue: 3,0:41:07.76,0:41:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你有这么多的资产
Dialogue: 2,0:41:07.76,0:41:10.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You have so many assets and properties.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:10.92,0:41:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我有什么? 
Dialogue: 2,0:41:10.92,0:41:12.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What do I have? An empty drum!
Dialogue: 3,0:41:16.68,0:41:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当你得不到保释的时候，感觉就像是世界末日
Dialogue: 2,0:41:16.68,0:41:19.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}When you were not getting bail, it felt like the end.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:21.96,0:41:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我也有家庭
Dialogue: 2,0:41:21.96,0:41:23.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I also have a family.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:24.00,0:41:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我必须为他们着想
Dialogue: 2,0:41:24.00,0:41:25.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have to think about them.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:28.92,0:41:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以我卖掉了所有的股票
Dialogue: 2,0:41:28.92,0:41:30.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, I sold off all those shares.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:31.00,0:41:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不管价值多少，我都保留了下来
Dialogue: 2,0:41:31.00,0:41:33.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Whatever amount I got, I kept.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:35.36,0:41:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[阿什温]“我们那么信任你! ”
Dialogue: 2,0:41:35.36,0:41:37.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ashwin] 'We trusted you so much!'
Dialogue: 3,0:41:37.68,0:41:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们像兄弟一样信任你
Dialogue: 2,0:41:37.68,0:41:39.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We believed in you like a brother.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:39.68,0:41:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就连我也把哈沙德当作兄弟
Dialogue: 2,0:41:39.68,0:41:42.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Even I had taken Harshad for a brother, Ashwin Bhai.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:42.44,0:41:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我相信他，加入了高摩资本
Dialogue: 2,0:41:42.44,0:41:46.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I believed in him, and joined Growmore.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:49.56,0:41:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你告诉阿什温
Dialogue: 2,0:41:49.56,0:41:50.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tell Ashwin Bhai...
Dialogue: 3,0:41:50.88,0:41:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当你来找我，让我加入高摩资本的时候
Dialogue: 2,0:41:50.88,0:41:52.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...when you came to me with the offer to join Growmore...
Dialogue: 3,0:41:52.44,0:41:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 你是怎么说的，你这个混蛋！
Dialogue: 2,0:41:52.44,0:41:54.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...what did you say, you m**********r!
Dialogue: 3,0:41:56.56,0:41:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你还记得吗？还是我来提醒你？
Dialogue: 2,0:41:56.56,0:41:58.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you remember or should I remind you?
Dialogue: 3,0:42:00.52,0:42:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你跟我说，“我想创造历史”
Dialogue: 2,0:42:00.52,0:42:03.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You told me, "I want to create history. "
Dialogue: 3,0:42:05.72,0:42:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“需要100名员工全力以赴... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:42:05.72,0:42:08.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"You need 100 employees who will give their 100 percent..."
Dialogue: 3,0:42:08.40,0:42:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... ... 那么，我百分之一千确定我将创造历史”
Dialogue: 2,0:42:08.40,0:42:10.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...then, I'm 1,000 percent sure I'll create history."
Dialogue: 3,0:42:12.84,0:42:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“但只有布尚 · 巴特才能成为这100人的指挥官”
Dialogue: 2,0:42:12.84,0:42:16.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"But only Bhushan Bhatt can be the commander of those 100 people."
Dialogue: 3,0:42:20.76,0:42:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我们是老搭档了”
Dialogue: 2,0:42:20.76,0:42:22.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"We are old partners."
Dialogue: 3,0:42:23.52,0:42:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“你想要什么我就给你什么，跟我一起干吧”
Dialogue: 2,0:42:23.52,0:42:26.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"You can take whatever you want. Join hands with me."
Dialogue: 3,0:42:28.28,0:42:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我与你同在
Dialogue: 2,0:42:28.28,0:42:29.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Bhushan] 'I joined hands with you.'
Dialogue: 3,0:42:34.52,0:42:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德，你创造了你的历史
Dialogue: 2,0:42:34.52,0:42:36.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad, you created your history.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:38.36,0:42:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我将成为历史
Dialogue: 2,0:42:38.36,0:42:40.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I was going to be history.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:43.36,0:42:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你让我成为公司的合伙人了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:42:43.36,0:42:44.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Did you make me a partner in the company?
Dialogue: 3,0:42:45.12,0:42:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别说合伙人了，你他妈的让我当办公室文员！
Dialogue: 2,0:42:45.12,0:42:50.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Forget partner, you f**king made me an office-clerk!
Dialogue: 3,0:42:52.56,0:42:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你有资格成为合伙人吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:42:52.56,0:42:54.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you even worthy of being a partner?
Dialogue: 3,0:42:56.92,0:42:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你有那个胆量吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:42:56.92,0:42:58.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you have the b**ls?
Dialogue: 3,0:42:59.92,0:43:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是个该死的懦夫
Dialogue: 2,0:42:59.92,0:43:02.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You are a f**king coward.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:06.12,0:43:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在哭什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:43:06.12,0:43:07.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And what are you crying about?
Dialogue: 3,0:43:08.44,0:43:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你也赚了很多钱啊
Dialogue: 2,0:43:08.44,0:43:10.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You haven't made less money. You too have minted a lot.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:14.44,0:43:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，布尚，我绝不会因为你再进监狱一次
Dialogue: 2,0:43:14.44,0:43:18.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look Bhushan, because of your f**k up, I'm not going to go to jail this time.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:20.48,0:43:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是个骗子，中央调查局会认为我又做了一个骗局
Dialogue: 2,0:43:20.48,0:43:23.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You a*****e, CBI will think that I've done another scam.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:28.20,0:43:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你以为我想坐牢吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:43:28.20,0:43:30.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you think I want to go to jail?
Dialogue: 3,0:43:30.84,0:43:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你应该进监狱
Dialogue: 2,0:43:30.84,0:43:31.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You deserve to be in jail.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:32.52,0:43:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-中央调查局会逮捕你的 -别用调查局威胁我！
Dialogue: 2,0:43:32.52,0:43:35.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- The CBI will arrest you. - Don't threaten me with CBI!
Dialogue: 3,0:43:35.60,0:43:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 布尚，你个混蛋!-阿什温
Dialogue: 2,0:43:35.60,0:43:38.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Bhushan, you m**********r! - Ashwin Bhai!
Dialogue: 3,0:43:40.04,0:43:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁会去把这件事告诉调查局？
Dialogue: 2,0:43:40.04,0:43:41.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who will tell CBI?
Dialogue: 3,0:43:43.16,0:43:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你们俩？
Dialogue: 2,0:43:43.16,0:43:44.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The two of you?
Dialogue: 3,0:43:45.48,0:43:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔兄弟？
Dialogue: 2,0:43:45.48,0:43:46.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mehta Brothers?
Dialogue: 3,0:43:50.16,0:43:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那句谚语怎么说了？
Dialogue: 2,0:43:50.16,0:43:51.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ashwin Bhai, what was that?
Dialogue: 3,0:43:52.84,0:43:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}五十步笑百步？
Dialogue: 2,0:43:52.84,0:43:56.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The pot calling the kettle black..?
Dialogue: 3,0:43:58.04,0:44:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你有这么多的幌子公司
Dialogue: 2,0:43:58.04,0:44:01.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You have so many front companies.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:02.60,0:44:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你把这么多股份转让给了他们
Dialogue: 2,0:44:02.60,0:44:05.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Bhushan] 'You have transferred so many shares to them.'
Dialogue: 3,0:44:08.00,0:44:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果加州调查局知道了这件事，对任何人都不会有好结果的，哈沙德
Dialogue: 2,0:44:08.00,0:44:10.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If CBI gets to know, it won't end well for anyone, Harshad.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:14.60,0:44:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果这些股票仍然下落不明，情况会更好
Dialogue: 2,0:44:14.60,0:44:17.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It would have been better if these shares had remained missing.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:18.08,0:44:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}布尚，我要我的钱
Dialogue: 2,0:44:18.08,0:44:20.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bhushan, I want my money.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:23.44,0:44:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不会给你的
Dialogue: 2,0:44:23.44,0:44:24.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You won't get it.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:26.28,0:44:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}明白吗？我绝不会给你
Dialogue: 2,0:44:26.28,0:44:28.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hmm? You won't get it.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:29.24,0:44:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}尽你所能
Dialogue: 2,0:44:29.24,0:44:31.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do what you can.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:32.32,0:44:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你有勇气去证明..
Dialogue: 2,0:44:32.32,0:44:33.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And if you have the b**ls then prove...
Dialogue: 3,0:44:33.96,0:44:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你拥有这些股份，去找法庭说明
Dialogue: 2,0:44:33.96,0:44:37.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...in court that you own these shares and take them back.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:37.28,0:44:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}滚出去! 
Dialogue: 2,0:44:37.28,0:44:39.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Get out! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 3,0:44:40.84,0:44:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}滚出去! 
Dialogue: 2,0:44:40.84,0:44:42.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ashwin] 'Get out! M**********r!'
Dialogue: 3,0:44:42.80,0:44:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}布尚，你这个混蛋! 我还在市场上
Dialogue: 2,0:44:42.80,0:44:46.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bhushan, you M**********r! I'm still in the market.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:46.96,0:44:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我要让你裸体游街示众
Dialogue: 2,0:44:46.96,0:44:48.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll have you paraded naked.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:52.76,0:44:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}该死的！
Dialogue: 2,0:44:52.76,0:44:54.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}F*****g b*****d!
Dialogue: 3,0:45:02.72,0:45:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，我是哈尔沙德公司一名忠诚的员工
Dialogue: 2,0:45:02.72,0:45:06.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, I'm an honest employee in Harshad's company...
Dialogue: 3,0:45:07.80,0:45:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我老板叫我做什么我就做什么
Dialogue: 2,0:45:07.80,0:45:10.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...I do what my boss asks me to.
Dialogue: 3,0:45:13.32,0:45:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是你的老板想要回那些从来没有记录在案的股份
Dialogue: 2,0:45:13.32,0:45:16.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But your boss wants those shares back which were never in the record.
Dialogue: 3,0:45:19.60,0:45:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你负责处理所有高摩的资产记录，对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:45:19.60,0:45:21.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You handle the records of all Growmore assets, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:45:23.92,0:45:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 不是吗? 告诉我-是的
Dialogue: 2,0:45:23.92,0:45:25.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Isn't it? Tell me. - Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:45:26.80,0:45:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那些股票是怎么消失的
Dialogue: 2,0:45:26.80,0:45:28.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Where have those shares disappeared...
Dialogue: 3,0:45:29.32,0:45:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么高摩和管理员都没有呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:45:29.32,0:45:32.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...if neither Growmore nor the custodian have them?
Dialogue: 3,0:45:37.72,0:45:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们兄弟俩已经在公开市场上秘密卖掉了所有的股票
Dialogue: 2,0:45:37.72,0:45:41.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The brothers have secretly sold all the shares in the open market.
Dialogue: 3,0:45:46.92,0:45:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，在1992年管理人扣押哈沙德的资产时
Dialogue: 2,0:45:46.92,0:45:51.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, in 1992 when the custodian attached Harshad's assets...
Dialogue: 3,0:45:53.52,0:45:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德根本没有申报这些股票
Dialogue: 2,0:45:53.52,0:45:56.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...Harshad did not declare those stocks.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:00.08,0:46:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他出狱后
Dialogue: 2,0:46:00.08,0:46:01.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And after he got out of jail...
Dialogue: 3,0:46:01.88,0:46:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他把所有的股份都转到了幌子公司
Dialogue: 2,0:46:01.88,0:46:04.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...he transferred all the shares to front companies.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:07.32,0:46:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在1993年到1995年之间
Dialogue: 2,0:46:07.32,0:46:10.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And between 1993 and 1995...
Dialogue: 3,0:46:12.68,0:46:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他悄悄把这些股票在市场上卖掉
Dialogue: 2,0:46:12.68,0:46:17.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...he gradually introduced these shares in the market and sold them.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:20.84,0:46:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果真的是这样
Dialogue: 2,0:46:20.84,0:46:23.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}When Harshad had not declared those shares...
Dialogue: 3,0:46:24.24,0:46:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他为什么要去找管理员？
Dialogue: 2,0:46:24.24,0:46:25.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...why did he go to the custodian?
Dialogue: 3,0:46:26.60,0:46:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，你了解哈沙德 · 梅塔吧
Dialogue: 2,0:46:26.60,0:46:28.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, you know Harshad Mehta.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:30.20,0:46:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他愚弄了所有人，从股票市场到首相
Dialogue: 2,0:46:30.20,0:46:33.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He has fooled everyone, from the share market to the Prime Minister.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:35.56,0:46:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这一次，他是想把责任都推到管理员身上，然后逃脱惩罚
Dialogue: 2,0:46:35.56,0:46:39.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This time too, he thought he'll blame it all on the custodian and get away with it.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:44.56,0:46:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是他的新骗局，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:46:44.56,0:46:46.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is his new scam, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:52.88,0:46:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[阿米塔布]“欢迎大家”
Dialogue: 2,0:46:52.88,0:46:55.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Amitabh] 'I welcome you all.'
Dialogue: 3,0:46:55.84,0:46:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}欢迎大家收看今天的节目
Dialogue: 2,0:46:55.84,0:46:58.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'I welcome you all to today's episode.'
Dialogue: 3,0:46:58.56,0:47:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我是阿米塔布·巴沙坎，你正在收看的是《谁能成为百万富翁》
Dialogue: 2,0:46:58.56,0:47:02.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'I am Amitabh Bachchan and you're watching "Kaun Banega Crorepati".'
Dialogue: 3,0:47:02.08,0:47:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谢谢
Dialogue: 2,0:47:02.08,0:47:02.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Thank you.'
Dialogue: 3,0:47:04.08,0:47:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}曾经有一段时间，我是市场上的巴沙坎
Dialogue: 2,0:47:04.08,0:47:06.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There was a time when I was the Bachchan of the market.
Dialogue: 3,0:47:07.12,0:47:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我曾为普通人赚了几百万
Dialogue: 2,0:47:07.12,0:47:09.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I used to earn millions for the common man.
Dialogue: 3,0:47:10.60,0:47:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在巴沙坎先生正在让普通人成为百万富翁
Dialogue: 2,0:47:10.60,0:47:12.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now Mr. Bachchan is making common men millionaires.
Dialogue: 3,0:47:15.28,0:47:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}即使是巴沙坎先生也不得不..
Dialogue: 2,0:47:15.28,0:47:17.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Even Mr. Bachchan had to move...
Dialogue: 3,0:47:17.44,0:47:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从大银幕搬到小银幕再次上演
Dialogue: 2,0:47:17.44,0:47:19.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...from the big screen to the small to make a comeback.
Dialogue: 3,0:47:22.28,0:47:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我们想再次东山再起，我们也应该从小处着手
Dialogue: 2,0:47:22.28,0:47:26.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If we want to make a comeback again, we should also start small.
Dialogue: 3,0:47:28.08,0:47:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好了，嫂子，你有什么要说的吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:47:28.08,0:47:29.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There you go. Bhabhi. Do you have anything to say?
Dialogue: 3,0:47:32.08,0:47:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}小事和大事一样危险
Dialogue: 2,0:47:32.08,0:47:33.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Small is as risky as big.
Dialogue: 3,0:47:35.40,0:47:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而风险是..
Dialogue: 2,0:47:35.40,0:47:36.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And risk is...
Dialogue: 3,0:47:36.80,0:47:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 生活的调味品！
Dialogue: 2,0:47:36.80,0:47:37.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the spice of life!
Dialogue: 3,0:47:38.68,0:47:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他不会改变的
Dialogue: 2,0:47:38.68,0:47:40.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He won't change.
Dialogue: 3,0:48:29.68,0:48:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你怎么就不明白呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:48:29.68,0:48:30.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why don't you understand?
Dialogue: 3,0:48:32.52,0:48:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我没有卖出任何匿名股票，这都是我的员工干的..
Dialogue: 2,0:48:32.52,0:48:35.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I haven't sold any anonymous shares. This is all my employee's doing...
Dialogue: 3,0:48:38.68,0:48:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你们这些白领罪犯，你们以为你们是谁？
Dialogue: 2,0:48:38.68,0:48:41.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You f**king white-collar criminals. Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 3,0:48:42.60,0:48:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你凌驾于这个体系之上吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:48:42.60,0:48:43.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you above the system?
Dialogue: 3,0:48:44.80,0:48:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你住在大房子里，开着豪华轿车
Dialogue: 2,0:48:44.80,0:48:47.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You live in big houses, drive luxurious cars.
Dialogue: 3,0:48:48.08,0:48:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样你就可以随便利用我们了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:48:48.08,0:48:49.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Does that give you the power to use us?
Dialogue: 3,0:48:51.20,0:48:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你这个混蛋，那么多人因为你而流落街头
Dialogue: 2,0:48:51.20,0:48:54.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You p**p, so many people are on the streets because of you.
Dialogue: 3,0:48:54.68,0:48:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么多人自杀，你这个混蛋！
Dialogue: 2,0:48:54.68,0:48:56.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So many people died, you m**********r!
Dialogue: 3,0:48:58.48,0:48:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}开始说吧
Dialogue: 2,0:48:58.48,0:48:59.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Start talking.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:00.44,0:49:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}坦白一切
Dialogue: 2,0:49:00.44,0:49:01.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Confess everything.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:02.76,0:49:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}告诉我真相
Dialogue: 2,0:49:02.76,0:49:03.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:04.92,0:49:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}否则，我会杀了你，把你埋在这里
Dialogue: 2,0:49:04.92,0:49:07.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Otherwise, I'll kill you and bury you right here.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:08.88,0:49:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}开始说吧！
Dialogue: 2,0:49:08.88,0:49:09.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Start talking!
Dialogue: 3,0:49:16.84,0:49:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别担心
Dialogue: 2,0:49:16.84,0:49:18.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ashwin] 'Don't worry.'
Dialogue: 3,0:49:21.12,0:49:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}特别法庭曾经因为马鲁蒂案判了你五年，记得吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:49:21.12,0:49:24.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The special court also gave you five years in the Maruti case, remember?
Dialogue: 3,0:49:25.56,0:49:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}发生什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:49:25.56,0:49:26.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Did anything happen then?
Dialogue: 3,0:49:27.32,0:49:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们把它上诉到了最高法院，不是吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:49:27.32,0:49:28.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We took it to the Supreme Court, didn't we?
Dialogue: 3,0:49:29.92,0:49:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这一次，他们也不能把你关在监狱里太久
Dialogue: 2,0:49:29.92,0:49:32.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This time too, they can't keep you in jail for long.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:33.84,0:49:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我出狱的那天..
Dialogue: 2,0:49:33.84,0:49:35.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The day I get out...
Dialogue: 3,0:49:36.68,0:49:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我要杀了布尚
Dialogue: 2,0:49:36.68,0:49:38.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...I'll f*****g kill Bhushan.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:38.20,0:49:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}忘了布尚吧
Dialogue: 2,0:49:38.20,0:49:39.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Forget Bhushan.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:40.56,0:49:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们以后再处理他
Dialogue: 2,0:49:40.56,0:49:41.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We'll handle him later.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:45.24,0:49:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，兄弟
Dialogue: 2,0:49:45.24,0:49:46.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Listen, Bhai.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:47.20,0:49:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会以你的身体情况为由申请保释
Dialogue: 2,0:49:47.20,0:49:49.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll get you bail on health grounds.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:50.20,0:49:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:49:50.20,0:49:51.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:49:52.28,0:49:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}中央调查局没有任何理由，也不能把你关在监狱里太久
Dialogue: 2,0:49:52.28,0:49:56.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And the CBI can't keep you in jail for long, without any reason.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:04.08,0:50:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你说话像个真正的律师
Dialogue: 2,0:50:04.08,0:50:05.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You're talking like a real lawyer.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:10.28,0:50:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是药..
Dialogue: 2,0:50:10.28,0:50:14.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This medicine...
Dialogue: 3,0:50:15.24,0:50:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}保重身体
Dialogue: 2,0:50:15.24,0:50:16.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Take care of your health.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:17.92,0:50:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}按时吃药
Dialogue: 2,0:50:17.92,0:50:19.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Take your medicine on time.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:19.96,0:50:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不要像我们小时候那样冲进马桶
Dialogue: 2,0:50:19.96,0:50:22.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't flush it down the toilet like you did when we were kids.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:23.20,0:50:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}乔蒂要你经常锻炼..
Dialogue: 2,0:50:23.20,0:50:25.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And Jyoti has asked you to exercise regularly...
Dialogue: 3,0:50:25.16,0:50:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会的，我会的
Dialogue: 2,0:50:25.16,0:50:26.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll do it, I will.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:37.48,0:50:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我走了
Dialogue: 2,0:50:37.48,0:50:38.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll leave now.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:41.32,0:50:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我很快就会拿到开庭日期
Dialogue: 2,0:50:41.32,0:50:43.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll get the date from the court soon.
Dialogue: 3,0:51:00.72,0:51:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别担心
Dialogue: 2,0:51:00.72,0:51:01.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 3,0:51:34.20,0:51:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}乔蒂..
Dialogue: 2,0:51:34.20,0:51:36.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Jyoti...
Dialogue: 3,0:51:41.24,0:51:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}给乔蒂打电话..
Dialogue: 2,0:51:41.24,0:51:42.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Call Jyoti...
Dialogue: 3,0:51:42.72,0:51:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生..
Dialogue: 2,0:51:42.72,0:51:44.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir...
Dialogue: 3,0:51:45.84,0:51:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}医生..
Dialogue: 2,0:51:45.84,0:51:47.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Doctor...
Dialogue: 3,0:51:51.92,0:51:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}乔蒂... 乔蒂！
Dialogue: 2,0:51:51.92,0:51:54.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Jyoti... Jyoti!
Dialogue: 3,0:52:57.64,0:53:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Sucheta ]“你的家人对这整个情况有什么反应? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:52:57.64,0:53:00.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'What's your family's reaction to this entire situation?'
Dialogue: 3,0:53:00.92,0:53:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我和我的家人有不同的观点
Dialogue: 2,0:53:00.92,0:53:03.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'My family and I have different points of view.'
Dialogue: 3,0:53:03.96,0:53:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我站在一边，抱着我的雄心和梦想... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:53:03.96,0:53:06.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'I am on one side, with my ambitions and dreams...'
Dialogue: 3,0:53:10.96,0:53:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“另一边是我的家人... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:53:10.96,0:53:12.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] '...and on the other, is my family...'
Dialogue: 3,0:53:12.72,0:53:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他总是阻止施展拳脚
Dialogue: 2,0:53:12.72,0:53:14.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...who always stop me from doing things.'
Dialogue: 3,0:53:15.28,0:53:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们现在应该怎么做? 为什么我们需要这么做？
Dialogue: 2,0:53:15.28,0:53:17.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'What should we do now? Why do we need to do it... how?'
Dialogue: 3,0:53:19.68,0:53:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这些案子又给了他们一个新的借口
Dialogue: 2,0:53:19.68,0:53:22.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'And these cases have given them another excuse.'
Dialogue: 3,0:53:24.32,0:53:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是你看，现在我明白他们说的是有道理的
Dialogue: 2,0:53:24.32,0:53:27.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'But you see, now I see a point in whatever they are saying.'
Dialogue: 3,0:53:28.12,0:53:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}除了几千万卢比，我不需要钱
Dialogue: 2,0:53:28.12,0:53:29.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Beyond a few crores, I don't need money.'
Dialogue: 3,0:53:31.44,0:53:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我对数字很在行”
Dialogue: 2,0:53:31.44,0:53:33.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'I'm brilliant with numbers.'
Dialogue: 3,0:53:34.00,0:53:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我知道，如果你不能控制你的钱... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:53:34.00,0:53:36.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'And I know, that if you don't control your money...
Dialogue: 3,0:53:36.32,0:53:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}它很快就会变成一个诅咒
Dialogue: 2,0:53:36.32,0:53:37.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...it can quickly become a curse.'
Dialogue: 3,0:53:38.64,0:53:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}它会给你带来负面的影响
Dialogue: 2,0:53:38.64,0:53:41.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'It starts giving you negative impact rather than positive.'
Dialogue: 3,0:53:42.76,0:53:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不想把这毒药传给我儿子
Dialogue: 2,0:53:42.76,0:53:45.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'And I don't want to pass this poison to my son.'
Dialogue: 3,0:53:46.32,0:53:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“钱确实可以变成毒药”
Dialogue: 2,0:53:46.32,0:53:48.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'It's true that money can turn into poison.'
