Dialogue: 3,0:55:32.56,0:55:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很多新规定
Dialogue: 2,0:55:32.56,0:55:33.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A lot changed.
Dialogue: 3,0:55:33.92,0:55:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然而，什么都没有发生
Dialogue: 2,0:55:33.92,0:55:36.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And yet, nothing did.
Dialogue: 3,0:55:36.48,0:55:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就像世界上其他地方一样，聪明的犯罪头脑..
Dialogue: 2,0:55:36.48,0:55:39.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Like anywhere else in the world, ingenious criminal minds...
