Dialogue: 3,0:56:41.72,0:56:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}阿什温·梅塔继续作为律师亲自处理所有案件
Dialogue: 3,0:56:47.52,0:56:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个骗局或者说违规行为，随便你怎么称呼..
Dialogue: 2,0:56:47.52,0:56:51.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This whole scam or whatever you call, irregularities...
Dialogue: 3,0:56:52.92,0:56:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是由任何一个人犯下的
Dialogue: 2,0:56:52.92,0:56:55.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...has been not committed by any one person...
Dialogue: 3,0:56:55.96,0:56:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}或者任何一群人
Dialogue: 2,0:56:55.96,0:56:57.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...or any one group of persons.
Dialogue: 3,0:56:58.64,0:57:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而是整个业务
Dialogue: 2,0:56:58.64,0:57:00.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It is the whole business.
Dialogue: 3,0:57:00.64,0:57:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}令人惊讶的是，我们提供给印度储备银行的证词就在那里
Dialogue: 2,0:57:00.64,0:57:04.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And to the surprise, even now the confession is there from the RBI.
Dialogue: 3,0:57:04.92,0:57:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们从去年就知情... 一年多了
Dialogue: 2,0:57:04.92,0:57:08.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That they were aware of it since last... more than a year.
Dialogue: 3,0:57:09.28,0:57:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以就算是监管机构也无法改变..
Dialogue: 2,0:57:09.28,0:57:10.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So even they couldn't change it...
Dialogue: 3,0:57:11.76,0:57:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}银行
Dialogue: 2,0:57:11.76,0:57:14.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...banks who were the deciding authority...
Dialogue: 3,0:57:15.40,0:57:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}才是那个..
Dialogue: 2,0:57:15.40,0:57:17.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...who are the one who had the...
Dialogue: 3,0:57:18.40,0:57:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在市场上有发言权的角色
Dialogue: 2,0:57:18.40,0:57:20.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...more of a say in the market.
Dialogue: 3,0:57:21.04,0:57:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}经纪人只是整个市场的一小部分
Dialogue: 2,0:57:21.04,0:57:25.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Brokers are the small segment of the whole market.
Dialogue: 3,0:57:26.44,0:57:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我只有一个请求
Dialogue: 2,0:57:26.44,0:57:28.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Only one and one...
Dialogue: 3,0:57:29.40,0:57:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就是..
Dialogue: 2,0:57:29.40,0:57:30.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...my request is...
Dialogue: 3,0:57:32.20,0:57:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不想要花束
Dialogue: 2,0:57:32.20,0:57:34.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...I don't want bouquets.
Dialogue: 3,0:57:34.92,0:57:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别在我身上下大赌注
Dialogue: 2,0:57:34.92,0:57:36.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't give me big bets.
Dialogue: 3,0:57:37.88,0:57:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}过山车坐得太刺激了
Dialogue: 2,0:57:37.88,0:57:41.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's too much of a swing from top to the bottom...
Dialogue: 3,0:57:41.00,0:57:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在跌落神坛，我不会说我是英雄
Dialogue: 2,0:57:41.00,0:57:44.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and again swinging back up. And I won't say I'm a hero.
Dialogue: 3,0:57:44.84,0:57:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我做我自己，我为我自己感到骄傲，仅此而已
Dialogue: 2,0:57:44.84,0:57:47.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let me be what I am and I am proud of what I am. That's all.